399
00:32:16.117 --> 00:32:18.652
BUNCH OF HOPHEADS. THEY
THINK THEY'RE SOMETHING SPECIAL.

400
00:32:19.938 --> 00:32:22.038
LISTEN TO THAT.
THAT'S A BAD JAM.

401
00:32:23.709 --> 00:32:26.342
REDNECK NOISE,
DUDE. THAT'S ALL IT IS.

402
00:32:26.411 --> 00:32:29.190
MAKE ABOUT AS MUCH
SENSE AS YOU DO.

403
00:32:29.214 --> 00:32:32.515
ALL THEM CHUCKS BE RAPPIN'
ABOUT HOW THEY LOSIN' THEIR HO',

404
00:32:32.584 --> 00:32:35.018
SAYIN' HOW THEY AIN'T
GOT NO BREAD FOR BEER.

405
00:32:36.555 --> 00:32:40.056
FUCK THAT HONKY SHIT! GIVE
ME SOME MOTOWN JAMS, DIG IT?

406
00:32:42.294 --> 00:32:44.861
MAN, WHAT ARE YOU
TALKIN' SHIT FOR, MAN?

407
00:32:44.929 --> 00:32:48.115
HEY, JUNIOR, YOU EVER SMOKE
ANY SHIT? <i>THAT'S RIGHT, DUDE.</i>

408
00:32:48.183 --> 00:32:52.368
YOU ALL BE TRYIN' TO KEEP THE BLACK
MAN DOWN AND STRING HIM OUT ON THAT SHIT,

409
00:32:52.437 --> 00:32:55.939
BUT THE TIME BE'S COMIN' WHEN
THE BLACK MAN THROW THAT YOKE OFF.

410
00:32:56.008 --> 00:32:59.042
SIMPLE. FREE YOUR MIND,
YOUR ASS WILL FOLLOW.

411
00:32:59.110 --> 00:33:01.010
YEAH, I COULD DIG IT, MAN.

412
00:33:01.079 --> 00:33:04.715
YOU SMOKE THAT SHIT, EVERYTHING KIND
OF GETS WEIRD, YOU KNOW WHAT I MEAN?

413
00:33:04.783 --> 00:33:07.651
YOU HEAR THAT STORY ABOUT THE
GOOKS PUTTIN' CHEMICALS IN THE GRASS...

414
00:33:07.719 --> 00:33:10.586
<i>SO WE DON'T FIGHT, SO
WE BECOME PACIFISTS?</i>

415
00:33:10.656 --> 00:33:13.656
YEAH, WELL, DON'T YOU WORRY,
BUNNY, 'CAUSE YOU'S A KILLER ANYWAY.

416
00:33:13.725 --> 00:33:16.592
YEAH, BUT I STILL LIKE A PIECE
OF PUSSY ONCE IN A WHILE.

417
00:33:16.662 --> 00:33:19.996
AIN'T NOTHIN' LIKE A PIECE OF
PUSSY, 'CEPT MAYBE THE INDY 500.

418
00:33:20.064 --> 00:33:23.266
ONLY WAY YOU GET SOME PUSSY IS
THE BITCH DIES AND WILLS IT TO YOU,

419
00:33:23.335 --> 00:33:25.685
AND THEN, MAYBE.

420
00:33:25.754 --> 00:33:28.588
[Laughing]

421
00:33:29.925 --> 00:33:32.025
HOW'S IT GOIN', BUNNY?

422
00:33:32.093 --> 00:33:34.260
L.T., CHECK IT OUT.

423
00:33:37.299 --> 00:33:40.400
YOU LIKE THAT? TERRIFIC.

424
00:33:40.469 --> 00:33:44.337
I'LL SEND IT HOME. HEY, JUNIOR.

425
00:33:45.440 --> 00:33:47.573
LIEUTENANT. HELLO, SIR.

426
00:33:49.744 --> 00:33:52.378
<i>[Radio Announcer] NEWS IS UP
AT 5:00 ON AFEN. STAY TUNED.</i>

427
00:33:52.447 --> 00:33:56.316
<i>WE GOT A BIG ONE FROM THE
FIRST CAMP... [Continues, Indistinct]</i>

428
00:33:56.384 --> 00:33:58.963
HEY, RODRIGUEZ. THAT'S
QUITE A SHRINE YOU GOT THERE.

429
00:33:58.987 --> 00:34:00.854
THANK YOU, SIR.

430
00:34:00.923 --> 00:34:02.917
YOU, UH, NEED ANYTHING?

431
00:34:02.941 --> 00:34:06.142
NO, SIR. [O'Neill] I GOT MY HANDS
AROUND THIS FLYBOY'S NECK.

432
00:34:06.211 --> 00:34:08.628
<i>NOW, THIS GUY IS EASILY
THREE, FOUR TIMES MY SIZE.</i>

433
00:34:08.696 --> 00:34:10.875
NO, NO, 'CAUSE I GOT HIM
IN THE O'NEILL DEATH GRIP.

434
00:34:10.899 --> 00:34:13.745
HE DOESN'T KNOW WHETHER TO
SHIT OR GO BLIND, FOR CHRISSAKE.

435
00:34:13.769 --> 00:34:16.247
WHAT DO YOU SAY THERE,
L.T.? HOW YOU DOIN', RED?

436
00:34:16.271 --> 00:34:19.550
OH, NOT GOOD, NOT GOOD. THIS
COCKSUCKER'S GOT EVERY CARD IN THE DECK.

437
00:34:19.574 --> 00:34:21.507
FULL HOUSE. HUH?

438
00:34:21.576 --> 00:34:23.944
LOOK LIKE YOU'RE DOIN'
ALL RIGHT, SERGEANT.

439
00:34:24.012 --> 00:34:25.745
YEAH, AND I AIN'T
EVEN CHEATIN' YET.

440
00:34:25.814 --> 00:34:28.381
HEY, UH, LIEUTENANT,
SOME KENTUCKY WINDAGE?

441
00:34:28.449 --> 00:34:30.983
OH. THANKS, SANDY.

442
00:34:32.037 --> 00:34:35.338
- PLAY, LIEUTENANT?
- AHH. NAH.

443
00:34:35.407 --> 00:34:37.640
WOULDN'T WANNA GET
RAPED BY YOU GUYS.

444
00:34:37.709 --> 00:34:41.911
WHY'S THAT, LIEUTENANT? WHAT
ARE YOU SAVING UP TO BE? JEWISH?

445
00:34:41.980 --> 00:34:45.431
<i>[Laughing] JEWISH!</i>

446
00:34:45.500 --> 00:34:47.729
<i>[Radio Announcer] VENEREAL
DISEASE IS NOTHING TO LAUGH ABOUT.</i>

447
00:34:47.753 --> 00:34:51.588
I GOTTA RUN. I'LL, UH,
CATCH YOU MEN LATER.

448
00:34:51.657 --> 00:34:53.573
ENJOY YOURSELVES TONIGHT.

449
00:34:53.642 --> 00:34:55.392
[Belching]

450
00:34:59.397 --> 00:35:01.832
WELL, THAT IS ONE
SORRY-ASS MOTHERFUCKER.

451
00:35:04.402 --> 00:35:06.953
WHAT DO YOU SAY THERE,
BOB? GUY LIKE THAT MAKE IT?

452
00:35:07.021 --> 00:35:09.300
YES OR NO. UH-HUH.

453
00:35:09.324 --> 00:35:12.575
UH-HUH. I HAVE TO TELL YOU,
THAT'S PRECISELY WHAT I SAW.

454
00:35:12.644 --> 00:35:15.145
I MEAN, SOMETIMES I JUST
LOOK AT A GUY AND I KNOW,

455
00:35:15.213 --> 00:35:17.241
"THIS FELLA'S NOT
GONNA MAKE IT."

456
00:35:17.265 --> 00:35:19.382
JUST NO FUCKIN' WAY.

457
00:35:21.536 --> 00:35:23.537
COME ON, NOW.

458
00:35:23.605 --> 00:35:25.539
<i>♪♪ [Radio]</i>

459
00:35:25.607 --> 00:35:30.143
<i>♪ DO DO DO DO DO
DO DO DO ♪</i> [King Howls]

460
00:35:30.211 --> 00:35:35.148
<i>♪ DO DO DO DO DO DO DO
DO DO DO ♪</i> COME ON, NOW!

461
00:35:35.216 --> 00:35:37.150
OH, I WANT SOME NOW.

462
00:35:37.218 --> 00:35:40.854
[Singing Along With Radio] ♪ PEOPLE
SAY I'M THE LIFE OF THE PARTY ♪

463
00:35:40.923 --> 00:35:44.190
♪ 'CAUSE I TELL A JOKE OR TWO ♪

464
00:35:45.644 --> 00:35:51.331
<i>♪ ALTHOUGH I MIGHT BE
LAUGHING LOUD AND HARDY ♪</i>

465
00:35:51.400 --> 00:35:54.684
<i>♪ DEEP INSIDE I'M BLUE ♪</i>

466
00:35:55.754 --> 00:36:00.156
♪ SO TAKE A GOOD
LOOK AT MY FACE ♪

467
00:36:00.224 --> 00:36:04.727
♪ YOU'LL SEE THE SMILE
LOOKS OUT OF PLACE ♪

468
00:36:04.796 --> 00:36:10.200
[Howling] ♪ IF YOU LOOK
CLOSER IT'S EASY TO TRACE ♪

469
00:36:10.269 --> 00:36:13.503
♪ THE TRACKS OF MY TEARS ♪

470
00:36:13.571 --> 00:36:16.239
YEAH! ♪ OH, YEAH ♪

471
00:36:16.308 --> 00:36:18.291
<i>♪ I NEED YOU ♪</i>
♪ NEED ♪

472
00:36:18.360 --> 00:36:21.060
<i>♪ NEED YOU ♪
♪ NEED YOU ♪♪</i>

473
00:36:21.129 --> 00:36:23.530
<i>[Howling]</i>

474
00:36:23.598 --> 00:36:26.949
<i>[Taylor] NEW YEAR'S DAY, 1968.</i>

475
00:36:27.018 --> 00:36:30.337
<i>JUST ANOTHER DAY. STAYIN' ALIVE.</i>

476
00:36:30.405 --> 00:36:32.567
<i>THERE'S BEEN A LOT OF MOVEMENT
NEAR THE CAMBODIAN BORDER.</i>

477
00:36:32.591 --> 00:36:35.325
<i>REGIMENTS OF
N.V.A. MOVIN' ACROSS.</i>

478
00:36:35.394 --> 00:36:37.793
<i>A LOT OF LITTLE
FIREFIGHTS, AMBUSHES.</i>

479
00:36:37.862 --> 00:36:40.406
<i>WE DROP A LOT OF BOMBS.
THEN WE WALK THROUGH</i>

480
00:36:40.430 --> 00:36:42.648
<i>THE JUNGLE LIKE
GHOSTS IN A LANDSCAPE.</i>

481
00:36:43.952 --> 00:36:46.652
<i>PSST. PSST!</i>

482
00:37:03.121 --> 00:37:05.388
BUNKER.

483
00:37:05.457 --> 00:37:07.957
WHERE?

484
00:37:27.195 --> 00:37:31.815
<i>[Man On Radio] BRAVO TWO, BRAVO TWO-FIVE.
WE GOT BEAUCOUP BUNKERS UP HERE. OVER.</i>

485
00:37:32.817 --> 00:37:34.895
<i>TWO-FIVE, TWO. ROGER.</i>

486
00:37:34.919 --> 00:37:38.119
<i>BUNKERS AT POINT. TWO
ACTUAL IS ON THE WAY.</i>

487
00:37:38.740 --> 00:37:41.441
<i>TWO, TWO-FIVE. ROGER
THAT. BRAVO TWO-FIVE OUT.</i>

488
00:38:19.080 --> 00:38:21.180
BRAVO SIX, BRAVO SIX, BRAVO TWO.

489
00:38:21.249 --> 00:38:23.482
BE ADVISED THERE IS A
BUNKER COMPLEX UP FRONT.

490
00:38:23.551 --> 00:38:26.302
<i>[Man On Radio] WE'RE ON
OUR WAY DOWN. OVER.</i>

491
00:38:28.589 --> 00:38:30.757
SEE YOU NEXT WEEK. [Chuckles]

492
00:38:43.821 --> 00:38:45.755
<i>[Man On Radio] BRAVO
TWO, THIS IS ALPHA.</i>

493
00:38:45.823 --> 00:38:50.527
<i>BE ADVISED WE'RE IN THE TUNNELS
AND ONE MAN DOWN AT THIS TIME.</i>

494
00:38:50.595 --> 00:38:54.297
TAYLOR, GET YOUR ASS UP ON
THAT FLANK ABOUT 50 METERS.

495
00:38:54.366 --> 00:38:57.467
WASHINGTON, YOU COVER THIS SIDE.

496
00:38:57.536 --> 00:38:59.469
YES, SIR. GET OFF
YOUR ASS, HAROLD.

497
00:38:59.538 --> 00:39:02.288
[Muttering] BUMMER.

498
00:39:54.593 --> 00:39:56.571
OH, CHRIST, LOOK
AT THAT, WILL YOU?

499
00:39:56.595 --> 00:39:59.662
THE TEAPOT'S STILL BOILIN'.
THEY WERE JUST HERE.

500
00:40:01.149 --> 00:40:04.300
THIS IS SPOOKY, SANDY.
LET'S GET OUTTA HERE.

501
00:41:11.970 --> 00:41:14.370
[Footsteps]

502
00:41:14.439 --> 00:41:17.190
<i>[Body Crashing]</i>

503
00:41:21.295 --> 00:41:24.096
<i>[Sal] WATCH IT. WATCH IT!</i>

504
00:41:32.307 --> 00:41:34.373
LOOK WHAT WE GOT, SAL.

505
00:41:34.442 --> 00:41:36.542
WE GOT MAPS.

506
00:41:38.346 --> 00:41:39.804
WE GOT S-2 STUFF...

507
00:41:39.828 --> 00:41:43.216
MAN, THIS IS GOOK STUFF!
LET'S GET OUTTA HERE!

508
00:41:43.285 --> 00:41:46.252
NO, SAL, THIS IS IMPORTANT.
THIS IS IMPORTANT.

509
00:41:51.109 --> 00:41:53.910
COME ON. LET'S LEAVE. LET'S GO.

510
00:41:53.978 --> 00:41:56.729
- [Click]
- BOOBY TRAP! GET DOWN!

511
00:42:02.737 --> 00:42:06.072
MEDIC!

512
00:42:07.291 --> 00:42:09.925
HOLY JEEZ!

513
00:42:23.374 --> 00:42:25.491
GODDAMN IT.

514
00:42:28.429 --> 00:42:30.513
WE GOT, UH...

515
00:42:30.582 --> 00:42:33.516
WE GOT TWO MEN DOWN,
SIR. THERE WAS AN EXPLOSION.

516
00:42:33.585 --> 00:42:35.885
[Stuttering] WE NEED
HELP, SIR, ASAP.

517
00:42:35.954 --> 00:42:39.622
MOVE YOUR ASS OUTTA HERE! LET'S
GO! ONE ROUND WILL GET ALL YOU GUYS!

518
00:42:39.691 --> 00:42:41.936
RODRIGUEZ, MOVE
IT! JUNIOR, LET'S GO!

519
00:42:41.960 --> 00:42:43.893
LIEUTENANT! WHAT?

520
00:42:43.961 --> 00:42:47.830
TELL SIX WE NEED ENGINEERS. THIS POS IS
CRAWLIN' WITH TRAPS. THEY'RE ON THEIR WAY.

521
00:42:47.899 --> 00:42:51.300
THE N.V.A. OUT OF HERE HAVE BEEN SPOTTED
IN THE VILLAGE HALF A CLICK DOWN THE RIVER.

522
00:42:51.369 --> 00:42:53.503
SIX SAYS WE GOTTA
GET THERE ASAP. OKAY.

523
00:42:53.571 --> 00:42:58.390
ALSO, LEAVE FOUR MEN HERE AND A
MEDIC, OKAY? MOVE IT OUT. ALL RIGHT.

524
00:43:21.866 --> 00:43:24.233
<i>[Warren] PULL THE
FLANKS IN! LET'S MOVE!</i>

525
00:43:26.921 --> 00:43:29.705
NOW, WHERE'S MANNY? MANNY!

526
00:43:29.774 --> 00:43:32.758
YO, MANNY! HEY,
WASHINGTON! MANNY!

527
00:43:33.928 --> 00:43:35.906
<i>HEY, MANNY! MANNY! MANNY!</i>

528
00:43:35.930 --> 00:43:37.863
<i>WASHINGTON! YO, MANNY!</i>

529
00:43:37.932 --> 00:43:39.999
MANNY, WHERE ARE YOU AT?

530
00:44:06.377 --> 00:44:08.344
<i>[Taylor] WE HAD TO GET TO
THE VILLAGE BEFORE DARK,</i>

531
00:44:08.412 --> 00:44:11.830
<i>SO WE LEFT ELIAS WITH SOME MEN TO KEEP
LOOKING AND TO WAIT FOR THE ENGINEERS,</i>

532
00:44:11.899 --> 00:44:14.350
<i>BUT IT WAS KING WHO FOUND HIM,</i>

533
00:44:14.419 --> 00:44:17.519
<i>ABOUT A THOUSAND YARDS
DOWNRIVER, NOT FAR FROM THE VILLAGE.</i>

534
00:44:20.792 --> 00:44:22.725
<i>[Flies Buzzing]</i>

535
00:44:22.794 --> 00:44:24.860
<i>IT WAS THE END OF THE MYSTERY.</i>

536
00:44:56.243 --> 00:44:58.310
THE MOTHERFUCKERS.

537
00:45:06.253 --> 00:45:09.221
<i>[Taylor] THE VILLAGE, WHICH HAD
STOOD FOR MAYBE A THOUSAND YEARS,</i>

538
00:45:09.290 --> 00:45:11.390
<i>DIDN'T KNOW WE WERE
COMING THAT DAY.</i>

539
00:45:11.459 --> 00:45:13.392
<i>IF THEY HAD, THEY
WOULD HAVE RUN.</i>

540
00:45:13.461 --> 00:45:16.362
<i>BARNES WAS AT THE
EYE OF OUR RAGE,</i>

541
00:45:16.447 --> 00:45:18.381
<i>AND THROUGH HIM,
OUR CAPTAIN AHAB,</i>

542
00:45:18.449 --> 00:45:21.083
<i>WE WOULD SET THINGS RIGHT AGAIN.</i>

543
00:45:21.151 --> 00:45:23.252
<i>THAT DAY, WE LOVED HIM.</i>

544
00:45:23.320 --> 00:45:26.154
<i>[Pigs Snorting,
Grunting, Squealing]</i>

545
00:45:26.223 --> 00:45:28.591
<i>DUNG LAI! DUNG LAI!</i>

546
00:45:28.659 --> 00:45:30.826
THERE THEY GO, SARGE.

547
00:45:36.467 --> 00:45:39.468
CHECK HIM OUT. <i>YEAH.
YOU GOT IT, SARGE.</i>

548
00:45:39.537 --> 00:45:42.382
TUBBS, EBENHOCK, LET'S GO.
<i>[Woman Shouting In Vietnamese]</i>

549
00:45:42.406 --> 00:45:46.258
[Shouting] GET THAT STUPID
LOOK OFF YOUR FACE!

550
00:45:48.796 --> 00:45:50.841
<i>[Barnes] SGT. O'NEILL, CLEAR
OUT THESE FUCKIN' HOOCHES.</i>

551
00:45:50.865 --> 00:45:53.633
HEY, PIGGY, PIGGY. HEY, PIG.

552
00:45:53.701 --> 00:45:56.252
<i>[Pig Squealing]</i>

553
00:45:58.406 --> 00:46:01.206
<i>[Barnes Shouting, Indistinct]</i>

554
00:46:01.275 --> 00:46:03.642
<i>SPREAD OUT ON THE
RIGHT! WATCH YOUR BACKS!</i>

555
00:46:03.711 --> 00:46:05.644
<i>LET'S GO! MUSTER 'EM UP!</i>

556
00:46:05.713 --> 00:46:08.514
<i>HEY, HEY, HEY!</i> WHAT
YOU GOT HERE, HUH?

557
00:46:08.583 --> 00:46:10.849
<i>[O'Neill] LET'S GO!
MUSTER 'EM UP HERE!</i>

558
00:46:10.918 --> 00:46:13.063
GET OVER THERE! MOVE IT!

559
00:46:13.087 --> 00:46:15.165
[Woman Shouting In
Vietnamese] <i>COME ON. LET'S GO.</i>

560
00:46:15.189 --> 00:46:18.623
OVER HERE! LET'S GO,
JUNIOR! BRING 'EM IN!

561
00:46:18.692 --> 00:46:20.687
<i>[O'Neill] GET THOSE
PEOPLE DOWN HERE!</i>

562
00:46:20.711 --> 00:46:22.745
<i>[Villagers, Soldiers Shouting]</i>

563
00:46:22.814 --> 00:46:24.880
<i>LA DAI! LA DAI!</i>

564
00:46:24.949 --> 00:46:28.000
GET OUT OF THERE, YOU
FUCK-HEADS! MOVE! [Gunshot]

565
00:46:28.069 --> 00:46:30.236
<i>LA DAI MOI!</i>

566
00:46:33.457 --> 00:46:35.537
[Woman Speaking Vietnamese]

567
00:46:37.662 --> 00:46:40.879
[Speaking Vietnamese]

568
00:46:40.948 --> 00:46:43.861
<i>[Woman Shouting In
Vietnamese]</i> [Barnes] COME ON!

569
00:46:43.885 --> 00:46:46.919
[Shouting In Vietnamese]

570
00:46:46.987 --> 00:46:48.988
<i>[Barnes] PUT 'EM IN THE PIGPEN!</i>

571
00:46:49.056 --> 00:46:53.459
[Vietnamese] SHUT UP!
GET BACK! SHUT UP!

572
00:46:53.528 --> 00:46:55.611
GIVE ME YOUR WILLIE PETE.

573
00:46:55.680 --> 00:46:58.959
[Women Shouting]
<i>[Big Harold] SHUT UP!</i>

574
00:46:58.983 --> 00:47:01.317
MOVE BACK!

575
00:47:01.386 --> 00:47:04.102
FIRE IN THE HOLE!

576
00:47:07.441 --> 00:47:10.843
<i>[Women, Soldiers Shouting]</i>

577
00:47:10.912 --> 00:47:15.097
[Shouting, Sobbing] SHUT UP!

578
00:47:15.166 --> 00:47:17.544
<i>SHUT UP! SHUT UP!</i>

579
00:47:17.568 --> 00:47:19.502
GET 'EM OUTTA HERE!

580
00:47:19.570 --> 00:47:21.570
OH, FUCK! WE GOT ONE!

581
00:47:24.509 --> 00:47:27.560
<i>LA DAI! LA DAI!</i> GET THE
FUCK OUTTA THE HOLE! MOVE!

582
00:47:27.629 --> 00:47:30.463
GET THE FUCK OUTTA THERE!
LET'S GO! COME ON, MOTHERFUCKER!

583
00:47:30.531 --> 00:47:33.043
BE COOL, BE COOL. THEY'RE
SCARED, MAN. THEY'RE SCARED.

584
00:47:33.067 --> 00:47:35.434
OH, THEY'RE SCARED,
HUH? WHAT ABOUT ME, MAN?

585
00:47:35.503 --> 00:47:37.570
WHAT ABOUT ME? I'M
SICK OF THIS FUCKING SHIT!

586
00:47:37.639 --> 00:47:39.772
COME ON, MOTHERFUCKER! MOVE!

587
00:47:39.840 --> 00:47:41.790
WATCH THIS FUCKER!

588
00:47:41.859 --> 00:47:44.921
<i>FUCKERS DON'T WANT US HERE. WHO
THE FUCK THEY THINK WE'RE FIGHTIN' FOR?</i>

589
00:47:44.945 --> 00:47:47.779
<i>GOT ONE MORE! HEY! HEY!</i> LA DAI!

590
00:47:47.848 --> 00:47:50.482
LA DAI! NO, NO, NO!
[Speaking Vietnamese]

591
00:47:50.551 --> 00:47:53.018
<i>DUNG BAN! DUNG BAN! [Vietnamese]</i>

592
00:47:53.087 --> 00:47:55.187
WELL, WELL. WHAT HAVE WE HERE?

593
00:47:57.491 --> 00:47:59.458
<i>[Soldier] WE HAVE
ONE, TWO, THREE,</i>

594
00:47:59.527 --> 00:48:02.762
<i>FOUR MAG .58
CZECHOSLOVAKIAN MACHINE GUNS.</i>

595
00:48:02.830 --> 00:48:05.965
WE GOT TWO, FOUR...

596
00:48:06.034 --> 00:48:10.036
BARNES, THEY GOT ENOUGH RICE HERE
TO FEED A WHOLE FUCKIN' REGIMENT.

597
00:48:10.104 --> 00:48:12.805
<i>[Man On Radio] SIX-TWO,
UH, BE ADVISED YOU GOT...</i>

598
00:48:12.874 --> 00:48:16.208
SGT. WARREN, YOU BRING THAT
HONCHO OVER HERE. YOU GOT IT.

599
00:48:16.277 --> 00:48:19.378
TUBBS, GET OUTTA
THERE! JUNIOR, BURN IT!

600
00:48:19.447 --> 00:48:22.765
WHAT THE FUCK'S THE MATTER
WITH YOU? I WASN'T GONNA HURT YOU.

601
00:48:22.833 --> 00:48:24.812
DID IT LOOK LIKE I WAS
GONNA FUCKIN' HURT YOU?

602
00:48:24.836 --> 00:48:27.270
WHY DIDN'T YOU LISTEN
TO ME, HUH? WHY?

603
00:48:27.338 --> 00:48:30.273
WHY DIDN'T YOU FUCKIN'
LISTEN TO ME? FUCKIN' STUPID?

604
00:48:30.325 --> 00:48:33.859
YOU STUPID ASSHOLE! GET THE
FUCK UP HERE! [Pleading In Vietnamese]

605
00:48:33.928 --> 00:48:36.395
COME HERE, MOTHERFUCKER!
WHAT ARE YOU SMILING AT?

606
00:48:36.463 --> 00:48:39.148
HUH? WHY THE FUCK
DIDN'T YOU LISTEN TO ME?

607
00:48:39.217 --> 00:48:42.517
- DO HIM, MAN! DO HIM!
- WHAT ARE YOU SMILING AT?

608
00:48:42.586 --> 00:48:45.854
YOU WANT SOMETHING TO SMILE AT?
HUH? YOU WANT SOMETHING TO SMILE AT?

609
00:48:45.923 --> 00:48:47.317
<i>MOTHERFUCKER! [Gunfire]</i>

610
00:48:47.341 --> 00:48:50.092
DANCE, MOTHERFUCKER!
<i>[Bunny] YEAH!</i>

611
00:48:50.161 --> 00:48:52.861
<i>[Bunny] DO HIM,
MAN! DO HIM! [Gunfire]</i>

612
00:48:52.930 --> 00:48:54.525
<i>DANCE, ONE-LEGGER!</i>

613
00:48:54.549 --> 00:48:56.989
DANCE! DANCE! [Pleading]

614
00:48:57.050 --> 00:49:01.453
HUH? HUH? DANCE,
ONE-LEGGED MOTHERFUCKER!

615
00:49:01.522 --> 00:49:04.562
[Shouting] <i>[Woman Sobbing]</i>

616
00:49:08.262 --> 00:49:10.395
<i>HEY, MAN, COME
ON. LET'S GO, MAN.</i>

617
00:49:10.464 --> 00:49:15.400
<i>[Woman Sobbing, Pleading]</i>

618
00:49:15.469 --> 00:49:18.838
FUCKIN' PUSSY, MAN!
HE'S LAUGHING AT YOU!

619
00:49:18.906 --> 00:49:21.440
<i>[Woman Pleading]</i> THAT'S
THE WAY THE GOOK LAUGHS.

620
00:49:22.576 --> 00:49:24.510
<i>YEAH, SURE YOU ARE.</i>

621
00:49:24.578 --> 00:49:26.645
YOU'RE REAL SORRY, AIN'T YA?

622
00:49:26.713 --> 00:49:30.816
YOU'RE JUST CRYIN' YOUR LITTLE HEARTS
OUT ABOUT SANDY AND SAL AND MANNY!

623
00:49:30.885 --> 00:49:32.879
<i>[Woman]</i> DUNG BAN! FORGET
ABOUT IT, BUNNY, HUH?

624
00:49:32.903 --> 00:49:35.338
LET'S GO. WHAT DO YOU SAY?

625
00:49:40.895 --> 00:49:44.663
- [O'Neill] COME ON.
- [Shouting]

626
00:49:44.732 --> 00:49:47.249
[Shouting In Vietnamese]

627
00:49:47.318 --> 00:49:50.836
<i>[Woman Shouting, Sobbing]</i>

628
00:49:50.905 --> 00:49:53.917
<i>[Bunny Grunting] [Woman]</i>
DUNG BAN! DUNG BAN!

629
00:49:53.941 --> 00:49:56.475
<i>[Woman Sobbing]</i> [Exhales]

630
00:49:56.544 --> 00:49:59.712
HOLY SHIT! YOU SEE THAT
FUCKIN' HEAD COME APART, MAN?

631
00:50:01.398 --> 00:50:04.398
<i>[Bunny] I NEVER SEEN BRAINS
LIKE THAT BEFORE, MAN.</i>

632
00:50:07.521 --> 00:50:10.789
I BET YOU THE OLD BITCH RUNS
THE WHOLE FUCKIN' SHOW, MAN.

633
00:50:10.858 --> 00:50:13.185
SHE PROBABLY CUT MANNY'S
THROAT. SHE'D PROBABLY

634
00:50:13.209 --> 00:50:15.160
CUT MY BALLS OFF IF
SHE HAD THE CHANCE.

635
00:50:15.229 --> 00:50:17.679
BUNNY, WE LEAVE NOW, AND
NOBODY SAW A FUCKIN' THING.

636
00:50:17.748 --> 00:50:20.560
YOU UNDERSTAND ME, TAYLOR?
NOT A FUCKIN' THING! FUCKIN' WOMAN!

637
00:50:20.584 --> 00:50:23.852
COME ON, MAN. LET'S FUCKIN' DO HER,
MAN. LET'S DO THIS WHOLE FUCKIN' VILLAGE!

638
00:50:25.273 --> 00:50:28.433
LOOK AT THE SCARS ON
THIS GOOK HONCHO, SARGE.

639
00:50:30.077 --> 00:50:32.211
GET OUTTA HERE, TUBBS.

640
00:50:34.581 --> 00:50:37.381
[Speaking Vietnamese] YEAH, YEAH,
YEAH, YEAH, YEAH, YEAH, YEAH.

641
00:50:41.455 --> 00:50:44.623
WHERE'D HE GET THESE
WOUNDS? [Speaking Vietnamese]

642
00:50:45.960 --> 00:50:49.328
[Vietnamese] SAYS HE WAS
HIT IN A BOMBING RAID.

643
00:50:49.396 --> 00:50:51.836
HE'S A DINK FOR SURE!

644
00:50:53.667 --> 00:50:55.600
ASK HIM WHY THOSE
WEAPONS WERE HERE.

645
00:50:55.669 --> 00:50:57.603
<i>[Lerner Questioning
In Vietnamese]</i>

646
00:50:57.671 --> 00:50:59.755
<i>[Village Chief Replies]</i>

647
00:50:59.824 --> 00:51:03.259
HE SAYS THEY HAD NO CHOICE. THE N.V.A.
KILLED THE OLD HONCHO WHEN HE SAID NO.

648
00:51:03.327 --> 00:51:07.563
HE SAYS ALL THE RICE IS
THEIRS. OH, BULLSHIT, LERNER!

649
00:51:07.632 --> 00:51:10.599
WHO THE HELL WAS THE GOOK
WE NAILED ON THE RIVERBANK?

650
00:51:10.668 --> 00:51:14.836
[Vietnamese] [Vietnamese]

651
00:51:17.642 --> 00:51:20.876
HE DOESN'T KNOW. HE SAYS THAT THE N.V.A.
AIN'T BEEN AROUND IN A COUPLE OF MONTHS.

652
00:51:20.944 --> 00:51:24.396
MAYBE IT WAS A SCOUT OR
SOMETHING, SARGE. YEAH, SURE, A SCOUT.

653
00:51:24.464 --> 00:51:27.482
WHAT ABOUT THE FUCKIN' RICE
AND THE WEAPONS? WHO THEY FOR?

654
00:51:28.485 --> 00:51:30.485
[Speaking Vietnamese]

655
00:51:30.554 --> 00:51:33.322
THAT COCKSUCKER KNOWS WHAT I'M
SAYING. HE UNDERSTANDS, DON'T YOU, POP?

656
00:51:33.391 --> 00:51:35.819
GODDAMN RIGHT HE DOES!
<i>[Barnes Shouting In Vietnamese]</i>

657
00:51:35.843 --> 00:51:39.278
- HE'S LYING THROUGH HIS TEETH!
- WASTE THE FUCKER. THEN SEE WHO TALKS.

658
00:51:39.347 --> 00:51:42.598
<i>- [Barnes Shouts In Vietnamese]</i>
<i>- [Lerner] HE SWEARS</i>
<i>HE DOESN'T KNOW ANYTHING!</i>

659
00:51:42.667 --> 00:51:44.900
[Speaking Vietnamese]

660
00:51:44.969 --> 00:51:47.937
[Both Shouting]

661
00:51:48.005 --> 00:51:49.983
HE SWEARS HE DOESN'T KNOW
ANYTHING. HE HATES THE N.V.A.

662
00:51:50.007 --> 00:51:53.659
THEY COME WHEN THEY WANT AND TAKE
THE PLACE OVER. WHAT'S THE BITCH SAYIN'?

663
00:51:53.728 --> 00:51:56.640
I DON'T KNOW. SHE'S GOIN' ON
ABOUT WHY WE KILLED THE PIGS.

664
00:51:56.664 --> 00:51:59.476
THEY'RE FARMERS. THEY GOTTA
MAKE A LIVIN', ALL THAT SHIT. AW, JESUS!

665
00:51:59.500 --> 00:52:03.402
<i>[Chief, Woman
Arguing In Vietnamese]</i>

666
00:52:07.024 --> 00:52:09.357
[Shouting] <i>[Barnes] SHUT UP!</i>

667
00:52:09.426 --> 00:52:12.010
- [Chief Shouting]
- SHUT THE FUCK UP!

668
00:52:12.079 --> 00:52:16.849
<i>[Chief, Woman Shouting]</i>

669
00:52:21.221 --> 00:52:23.855
[Child Wailing]

670
00:52:26.544 --> 00:52:28.877
<i>[Wailing Continues]</i>

671
00:52:28.946 --> 00:52:33.616
[Crying, Shouting In Vietnamese]

672
00:52:36.437 --> 00:52:40.439
<i>YOU TELL HIM HE STARTS TALKIN',
OR I'M GONNA WASTE MORE OF 'EM.</i>

673
00:52:40.507 --> 00:52:42.707
TELL HIM, LERNER!

674
00:52:42.776 --> 00:52:45.009
<i>[Child Wailing] [Chief Gasps]</i>

675
00:52:45.078 --> 00:52:47.429
[Speaking Vietnamese]

676
00:52:47.498 --> 00:52:49.125
<i>[Lerner, Chief
Shouting]</i> HEY, SARGE!

677
00:52:49.149 --> 00:52:51.750
LET US IN ON THIS, ALL RIGHT?

678
00:52:56.007 --> 00:52:57.889
<i>[Child Wailing] [Tony]
LET'S GO FOR IT.</i>

679
00:52:57.958 --> 00:53:02.394
LET'S DO THE WHOLE FUCKIN' VILLAGE!
COME ON, SARGE! WHAT ARE WE WAITING FOR?

680
00:53:02.463 --> 00:53:06.331
[Wailing]

681
00:53:06.400 --> 00:53:08.683
LET'S DO 'EM! OUTTA MY WAY!

682
00:53:08.752 --> 00:53:11.437
[Wailing]

683
00:53:11.505 --> 00:53:13.939
THIS IS HIS DAUGHTER,
RIGHT? RIGHT?

684
00:53:15.076 --> 00:53:17.025
<i>[Chief Shouting]</i>

685
00:53:17.094 --> 00:53:19.928
<i>[Girl Shouting]</i>

686
00:53:19.997 --> 00:53:22.815
[Wailing]

687
00:53:22.883 --> 00:53:25.434
YOU LIE! NO, YOU
LIE! [Vietnamese]

688
00:53:25.502 --> 00:53:30.372
YOU V.C.! [Speaking Vietnamese]

689
00:53:30.440 --> 00:53:33.959
- [Vietnamese]
- [Vietnamese]

690
00:53:35.095 --> 00:53:37.579
<i>BARNES!</i>

691
00:53:38.916 --> 00:53:41.483
BARNES!

692
00:53:44.822 --> 00:53:47.189
WHAT THE FUCK DO
YOU THINK YOU'RE DOING?

693
00:53:50.977 --> 00:53:53.428
STAY OUT OF THIS, ELIAS.
THIS AIN'T YOUR SHOW.

694
00:53:53.497 --> 00:53:56.748
YOU AIN'T A FIRING
SQUAD, YOU PIECE OF SHIT!

695
00:53:56.817 --> 00:54:00.235
<i>GET HIM, BARNES!
GET HIM, BARNES!</i>

696
00:54:00.304 --> 00:54:02.988
ELIAS, NO! NO, NO!

697
00:54:03.057 --> 00:54:05.657
<i>GET HIM! GET HIM! TEAR
HIS FUCKIN' HEAD OFF!</i>

698
00:54:05.726 --> 00:54:08.994
- [Elias Grunting]
- [Shouting, Indistinct]

699
00:54:12.133 --> 00:54:16.268
<i>COME ON, ELIAS! SEND HIM TO
HELL! SEND HIM TO HELL, ELIAS!</i>

700
00:54:16.337 --> 00:54:19.138
GET HIM! <i>[Lieutenant]
BREAK IT UP NOW!</i>

701
00:54:19.206 --> 00:54:22.775
[Soldiers Shouting]

702
00:54:22.843 --> 00:54:25.327
BREAK IT UP, FELLAS!

703
00:54:25.396 --> 00:54:29.448
[Grunting] BREAK IT UP!

704
00:54:29.517 --> 00:54:31.528
[Grunting] COME
ON, ELIAS! CHILL!

705
00:54:31.552 --> 00:54:35.787
YOU'RE DEAD, ELIAS! I SWEAR
TO FUCKIN' GOD YOU'RE DEAD!

706
00:54:35.856 --> 00:54:39.508
YOU! YOU'RE GONNA
DO TIME IN L.B.J.!

707
00:54:39.576 --> 00:54:42.126
THIS SHIT WON'T WASH,
YOU FUCKIN' PUKE!

708
00:54:42.195 --> 00:54:46.448
BREAK IT UP! SHUT
UP! BREAK IT UP!

709
00:54:46.517 --> 00:54:48.450
LISTEN UP!

710
00:54:48.519 --> 00:54:50.919
CAPTAIN SAYS TO TORCH
THIS PLACE! YOU HEAR THAT?

711
00:54:50.988 --> 00:54:54.172
TORCH THIS PLACE! BLOW
THE WEAPONS IN PLACE!

712
00:54:54.241 --> 00:54:57.270
<i>ROUND UP ALL SUSPECTED
V.C. AND SHAKE IT UP!</i>

713
00:54:57.294 --> 00:55:00.011
<i>WE AIN'T GOT MUCH
LIGHT LEFT.</i> LIEUTENANT,

714
00:55:00.080 --> 00:55:02.192
WHY THE FUCK DIDN'T
YOU DO SOMETHING?

715
00:55:02.216 --> 00:55:04.149
<i>WHAT ARE YOU TALKIN' ABOUT?</i>

716
00:55:04.218 --> 00:55:06.635
YOU KNOW WHAT THE
FUCK I'M TALKIN' ABOUT!

717
00:55:06.704 --> 00:55:10.922
NO, I DON'T! I DON'T KNOW WHAT
THE FUCK YOU'RE TALKIN' ABOUT, ELIAS!

718
00:55:15.428 --> 00:55:17.868
ALL RIGHT, MOVE IT OUT! LET'S
GO! YOU HEARD THE LIEUTENANT!

719
00:55:17.932 --> 00:55:21.032
MOVE IT OUT! TAYLOR,
LET'S GO, FOR CHRISSAKE!

720
00:55:21.101 --> 00:55:23.279
<i>[O'Neill] MOVE IT OUT! POLICE
UP THE WEAPONS! LET'S GO!</i>

721
00:55:23.303 --> 00:55:25.303
<i>[Francis] COME ON, HAROLD.</i>

722
00:56:00.357 --> 00:56:02.357
FIRE IN THE HOLE!

723
00:56:11.518 --> 00:56:13.718
FIRE IN THE HOLE!

724
00:56:17.825 --> 00:56:21.476
[No Audible Dialogue]

725
00:56:42.199 --> 00:56:44.733
<i>[Girl Screaming]</i>

726
00:56:58.783 --> 00:57:03.001
HEY, HEY, COME ON! MOREHOUSE,
YOU FUCKER! GET OUTTA HERE!

727
00:57:03.070 --> 00:57:05.520
GET THE FUCK OFF! DON'T DO IT!

728
00:57:05.589 --> 00:57:08.022
DON'T DO IT! YOU FUCKER!

729
00:57:08.091 --> 00:57:10.208
WHAT IS THIS, HUH?

730
00:57:14.681 --> 00:57:17.494
YOU A HOMOSEXUAL, TAYLOR?
WHAT THE FUCK IS YOUR PROBLEM?

731
00:57:17.518 --> 00:57:21.670
SHE'S A FUCKIN' DINK! SHE'S
A FUCKIN' HUMAN BEING, MAN!

732
00:57:21.738 --> 00:57:24.907
FUCK YOU! <i>[Tony] YOU'RE
A FUCKIN' CHERRY, TAYLOR!</i>

733
00:57:24.975 --> 00:57:26.942
FUCKIN' ANIMALS!

734
00:57:27.011 --> 00:57:29.144
ALL OF YOU, YOU'RE
FUCKIN' ANIMALS!

735
00:57:29.213 --> 00:57:31.213
FUCKIN' LAME FUCK!

736
00:57:31.282 --> 00:57:34.127
<i>[Tony] YOU DON'T BELONG IN THE
'NAM. THIS AIN'T YOUR PLACE AT ALL.</i>

737
00:57:34.151 --> 00:57:37.252
YOU DON'T FUCKIN' GET IT,
DO YOU, MAN? <i>[Morehouse Spits]</i>

738
00:57:37.321 --> 00:57:39.854
[Sobbing] YOU JUST
DON'T FUCKIN' GET IT.

739
00:57:40.857 --> 00:57:42.791
IT'S OKAY.

740
00:57:42.859 --> 00:57:44.910
[Sobbing]

741
00:57:45.913 --> 00:57:48.646
GET OUT OF THERE!

742
00:57:48.715 --> 00:57:50.966
<i>[Bunny] FUCK YOU, MAN!</i>

743
00:57:51.035 --> 00:57:54.235
[Laughing] COME ON, GUYS. POLICE
UP YOUR DICKS. LET'S GET OUTTA HERE.

744
00:57:58.141 --> 00:58:02.060
<i>[Villagers Shouting]</i>

745
00:58:50.794 --> 00:58:53.211
I DIDN'T SEE
ANYTHING, SIR. I DID.

746
00:58:53.280 --> 00:58:56.047
THAT DINK WAS REPORTED TO ME
AS N.V.A. BY SERGEANT BARNES, SIR.

747
00:58:56.116 --> 00:58:58.094
MY REPORT, SIR, WILL
INCLUDE LIEUTENANT WOLFE...

748
00:58:58.118 --> 00:59:00.184
AS BEING WITNESS
TO THE SHOOTING.

749
00:59:00.254 --> 00:59:03.488
ALL RIGHT, ELIAS. STAFF
SERGEANT BARNES.

750
00:59:03.557 --> 00:59:05.507
SIR.

751
00:59:05.575 --> 00:59:08.410
<i>I WANT A FULL REPORT FROM YOU ON
THIS WHEN WE GET BACK TO THE C.P.</i>

752
00:59:08.479 --> 00:59:10.457
YOU GOT IT, <i>DAI WEE,</i>

753
00:59:10.481 --> 00:59:12.858
AND I CAN THROW IN PLENTY OF
EYEWITNESSES IF YOU WANT, SIR.

754
00:59:12.882 --> 00:59:15.367
NOT NOW, GODDAMN IT. NOT NOW.

755
00:59:15.436 --> 00:59:17.735
WE'LL GET INTO THIS WHEN WE
GET BACK TO THE BASE CAMP.

756
00:59:17.804 --> 00:59:19.737
AND I CAN PROMISE YOU SOMETHING.

757
00:59:19.806 --> 00:59:22.240
IF I FIND OUT THERE
WAS AN ILLEGAL KILLING,

758
00:59:22.309 --> 00:59:24.242
THERE WILL BE A COURT-MARTIAL.

759
00:59:24.311 --> 00:59:26.577
RIGHT NOW I NEED
EVERY MAN IN THE FIELD,

760
00:59:26.646 --> 00:59:29.080
AND YOU TWO WILL CEASE FIRE.

761
00:59:29.149 --> 00:59:31.082
STAFF SERGEANT BARNES,

762
00:59:31.151 --> 00:59:33.168
SERGEANT ELIAS, YOU HEAR ME?

763
00:59:33.236 --> 00:59:35.170
YES, SIR. <i>YES, SIR.</i>

764
00:59:35.238 --> 00:59:37.121
<i>NOW, WE'RE GOING BACK
INTO THAT N.V.A. BUNKER</i>

765
00:59:37.145 --> 00:59:38.924
<i>COMPLEX TOMORROW,
THIS TIME FROM THE EAST.</i>

766
00:59:38.993 --> 00:59:40.926
YOU PEOPLE GET SOME REST...

767
00:59:40.994 --> 00:59:43.394
AND BE BACK UP HERE AT THE
C.P. AT 1900 FOR A BRIEFING.

768
00:59:43.464 --> 00:59:45.463
<i>YES, SIR.</i> YES, SIR.

769
00:59:50.270 --> 00:59:52.220
COME ON, MAN.

770
00:59:52.288 --> 00:59:55.556
YOU THINK THESE CHUCKS
GIVE A FUCK ABOUT YOU AND ME?

771
00:59:55.625 --> 00:59:59.227
COULD JUST AS WELL HAVE BEEN
YOU, HAROLD, YOU GOT IN BARNES'S WAY.

772
00:59:59.295 --> 01:00:01.229
AND THAT BUNNY?

773
01:00:01.297 --> 01:00:03.231
THAT MOTHERFUCKER'S CRAZY.

774
01:00:03.299 --> 01:00:05.250
I MEAN, HE SCARES ME, MAN.

775
01:00:05.319 --> 01:00:08.219
HE JUST SCARES ME. LOOK.

776
01:00:08.289 --> 01:00:11.390
YOU BLOODS ARE GETTING
TOO HUNG UP ON ALL THIS SHIT.

777
01:00:11.458 --> 01:00:14.225
THESE GOOKS ARE A LOT
SMARTER THAN YOU THINK.

778
01:00:14.295 --> 01:00:16.395
YOU KNOW, BARNES
KNOWS HIS SHIT, MAN.

779
01:00:16.463 --> 01:00:20.215
THEY WAS N.V.A., EVERY
LAST ONE OF THEM.

780
01:00:20.284 --> 01:00:22.250
NOW HE'S TAKEN
US THIS FAR, RIGHT?

781
01:00:22.319 --> 01:00:24.597
HE'LL TAKE US THE REST OF
THE WAY. <i>I DON'T KNOW, HOMES.</i>

782
01:00:24.621 --> 01:00:28.924
I MEAN, A CHRISTIAN DON'T GO AROUND
A VILLAGE CUTTING OFF HEADS AND SHIT.

783
01:00:28.992 --> 01:00:30.970
SHIT IS REALLY GETTING
OUT OF HAND, MAN.

784
01:00:30.994 --> 01:00:32.972
IT'S BLOWIN' WAY OUT OF CONTROL.

785
01:00:32.996 --> 01:00:36.147
IT SEEMS TO ME THAT YOU DON'T
SEEM TO KNOW THE DIFFERENCE...

786
01:00:36.216 --> 01:00:39.000
<i>THE WAY YOU SHOOT UP
THAT SHIT ALL THE TIME.</i>

787
01:00:39.069 --> 01:00:42.420
I DON'T KNOW, BROTHERS,

788
01:00:42.489 --> 01:00:45.657
BUT I'M HURTING REAL BAD INSIDE.

789
01:00:47.795 --> 01:00:51.213
DON'T WORRY ABOUT IT, SERGEANT.
ELIAS WON'T BE ABLE TO PROVE A THING.

790
01:00:51.281 --> 01:00:54.549
I MEAN, HE'S A TROUBLEMAKER.
HE... ELIAS IS A WATER WALKER.

791
01:00:54.618 --> 01:00:57.597
LIKE THEM POLITICIANS IN
WASHINGTON TRYING TO FIGHT THIS WAR...

792
01:00:57.621 --> 01:01:00.555
WITH ONE HAND TIED
AROUND THEIR BALLS.

793
01:01:00.624 --> 01:01:03.291
AIN'T NO NEED OR TIME FOR
A COURTROOM OUT HERE.

794
01:01:05.295 --> 01:01:07.629
<i>SARGE.</i> THANKS, BUN.

795
01:01:08.632 --> 01:01:10.899
HOW'D IT GO THERE, BOB?

796
01:01:10.968 --> 01:01:12.901
AAH.

797
01:01:12.970 --> 01:01:14.903
YEAH. THATAWAY, SARGE.

798
01:01:14.972 --> 01:01:16.949
FUCKING ELIAS, MAN.

799
01:01:16.973 --> 01:01:19.118
HE'S A FUCKING RAT,
THAT'S WHAT HE IS.

800
01:01:19.142 --> 01:01:21.954
HE'S GONNA GET EVERYBODY
IN THIS PLATOON IN DEEP SHIT.

801
01:01:21.978 --> 01:01:24.879
<i>SOMEBODY OUGHT TO FRAG HIS ASS.</i>

802
01:01:24.948 --> 01:01:26.909
SO WHAT DO YOU THINK THERE, BOB?

803
01:01:26.933 --> 01:01:28.911
GONNA BE AN
INVESTIGATION OR WHAT?

804
01:01:28.935 --> 01:01:31.453
<i>BOB?</i>

805
01:01:31.522 --> 01:01:34.756
<i>[Bunny] O'NEILL, MAN,
YOU WORRY TOO MUCH.</i>

806
01:01:34.825 --> 01:01:36.991
<i>SARGE WILL TAKE CARE OF IT.</i>

807
01:01:42.649 --> 01:01:44.609
<i>[Taylor] IT'S A BEAUTIFUL NIGHT.</i>

808
01:01:44.651 --> 01:01:47.686
<i>[Elias] YEAH, I LOVE
THIS PLACE AT NIGHT...</i>

809
01:01:47.755 --> 01:01:50.422
THE STARS.

810
01:01:51.925 --> 01:01:54.603
THERE'S NO RIGHT
OR WRONG IN THEM.

811
01:01:54.627 --> 01:01:56.695
<i>THEY'RE JUST THERE.</i>

812
01:01:56.763 --> 01:01:59.764
THAT'S A NICE WAY OF PUTTING IT.

813
01:02:03.436 --> 01:02:05.615
BARNES HAS GOT IT IN
FOR YOU, DOESN'T HE?

814
01:02:05.639 --> 01:02:08.272
BARNES BELIEVES
IN WHAT HE'S DOING.

815
01:02:09.943 --> 01:02:12.611
<i>AND YOU? DO YOU BELIEVE?</i>

816
01:02:15.616 --> 01:02:18.950
IN '65, YEAH.

817
01:02:20.120 --> 01:02:23.554
NOW,

818
01:02:23.624 --> 01:02:25.957
NO.

819
01:02:28.461 --> 01:02:32.063
WHAT HAPPENED TODAY
IS JUST THE BEGINNING.

820
01:02:32.132 --> 01:02:34.766
WE'RE GONNA LOSE THIS WAR.

821
01:02:34.835 --> 01:02:37.235
COME ON.

822
01:02:37.303 --> 01:02:40.105
YOU REALLY THINK SO? HONEST?

823
01:02:40.173 --> 01:02:43.407
WE'VE BEEN KICKING OTHER
PEOPLE'S ASSES FOR SO LONG...

824
01:02:43.476 --> 01:02:46.277
I FIGURE IT'S TIME
WE GOT OURS KICKED.

825
01:02:55.671 --> 01:02:57.855
<i>[Taylor] DAY BY DAY,</i>

826
01:02:57.924 --> 01:03:00.525
<i>I STRUGGLE TO MAINTAIN
NOT ONLY MY STRENGTH...</i>

827
01:03:00.594 --> 01:03:02.527
<i>BUT MY SANITY.</i>

828
01:03:02.596 --> 01:03:06.364
<i>IT'S ALL A BLUR. I HAVE
NO ENERGY TO WRITE.</i>

829
01:03:06.433 --> 01:03:09.534
<i>I DON'T KNOW WHAT'S RIGHT
AND WHAT'S WRONG ANYMORE.</i>

830
01:03:09.603 --> 01:03:11.536
<i>THE MORALE OF THE MEN IS LOW...</i>

831
01:03:11.605 --> 01:03:13.538
<i>A CIVIL WAR IN THE PLATOON,</i>

832
01:03:13.607 --> 01:03:16.073
<i>HALF THE MEN WITH
ELIAS, HALF WITH BARNES.</i>

833
01:03:16.142 --> 01:03:19.227
<i>THERE'S A LOT OF
SUSPICION AND HATE.</i>

834
01:03:19.296 --> 01:03:21.229
<i>I CAN'T BELIEVE WE'RE
FIGHTING EACH OTHER...</i>

835
01:03:21.298 --> 01:03:23.798
<i>WHEN WE SHOULD BE FIGHTING THEM.</i>

836
01:03:25.219 --> 01:03:27.552
<i>COUNTING DAYS AND THE SIX
INCHES IN FRONT OF MY FACE,</i>

837
01:03:27.620 --> 01:03:30.221
<i>NOT MUCH ELSE.</i>

838
01:03:30.290 --> 01:03:32.723
<i>HOPE THINGS ARE WELL, GRANDMA.</i>

839
01:03:32.792 --> 01:03:34.892
<i>TELL MOM AND DAD I...</i>

840
01:03:34.961 --> 01:03:37.228
<i>WELL, JUST TELL THEM.</i>

841
01:03:37.297 --> 01:03:39.297
<i>CHRIS.</i>

842
01:03:59.836 --> 01:04:01.770
[King] HEY, BIG BOY.

843
01:04:01.838 --> 01:04:04.538
I KNOW YOU THOUGHT YOU HAD
THAT LAUNDRY GIG ALL LAID OUT.

844
01:04:04.607 --> 01:04:07.876
I GOTTA PAINT MYSELF WHITE JUST
TO GET ME ONE OF THEM FUCKING JOBS.

845
01:04:07.944 --> 01:04:10.422
IT'S ALL RIGHT. I GOT MY
REQUEST IN FOR A CIRCUMCISION.

846
01:04:10.446 --> 01:04:12.558
I'M GONNA GET MY ASS
OUT OF THIS PLACE. [Laughing]

847
01:04:12.582 --> 01:04:14.866
<i>[King] WHAT YOU GONNA
DO? BECOME A RABBI?</i>

848
01:04:14.935 --> 01:04:16.935
LEECH.

849
01:04:18.438 --> 01:04:20.371
[Chuckles]

850
01:04:20.440 --> 01:04:22.941
<i>ALL RIGHT. MOVE IT OUT.</i>

851
01:04:26.112 --> 01:04:29.180
DON'T DRINK THAT, ASSHOLE.
YOU'RE GONNA GET MALARIA.

852
01:04:29.248 --> 01:04:31.182
YEAH, I HOPE SO.

853
01:04:31.251 --> 01:04:33.284
LET'S GO.

854
01:05:06.602 --> 01:05:09.137
<i>[Gunshots]</i>

855
01:05:10.673 --> 01:05:13.873
DOC! GET UP HERE! LERNER'S HIT!

856
01:05:18.832 --> 01:05:20.966
SERGEANT WARREN'S HIT.

857
01:05:24.454 --> 01:05:26.432
WHAT THE FUCK'S GOING ON?

858
01:05:26.456 --> 01:05:29.891
THEY GOT R.P.G.s, MAN. IT'S AN AMBUSH.
THEY WERE JUST WAITING FOR US HERE.

859
01:05:29.959 --> 01:05:32.059
WHO'S ON POINT?
LERNER AND WARREN.

860
01:05:32.128 --> 01:05:34.128
TAYLOR, WHERE YOU GOING?

861
01:05:37.768 --> 01:05:39.779
GODDAMN IT, YOU ASSHOLES.

862
01:05:39.803 --> 01:05:41.753
GET SOME FIREPOWER UP THERE.

863
01:05:41.822 --> 01:05:44.456
READY.

864
01:05:52.248 --> 01:05:54.648
WATCH OUT! ROCKETS!

865
01:06:02.408 --> 01:06:04.386
WHERE THE FUCK IS LERNER?

866
01:06:04.410 --> 01:06:07.228
[Whimpering] HE'S OVER
THERE BY THE LOG.

867
01:06:30.253 --> 01:06:34.722
FIRE MISSION. GRID: 6-4-9-4-0-2.

868
01:06:34.790 --> 01:06:36.768
DIRECTION: 6-1-0-0...

869
01:06:36.792 --> 01:06:39.544
<i>[Explosion]</i> ADJUST FIRE. OVER.

870
01:06:41.614 --> 01:06:44.599
LIEUTENANT, THEY'RE GONNA
GET IN TIGHT UNDER THE ARTY.

871
01:06:44.667 --> 01:06:47.835
I SPOTTED A CUT OVER THERE. LET ME
GET SOME MEN AND ROLL UP THAT FLANK.

872
01:06:47.904 --> 01:06:49.882
I CAN WORK RIGHT UP
ON THEM. GET ME BARNES.

873
01:06:49.906 --> 01:06:53.474
LOOK, ELIAS. WE GOT FOUR DOWN. WHAT DO
YOU WANT ME TO DO? FUCK YOU, LIEUTENANT.

874
01:06:53.543 --> 01:06:55.510
<i>[Explosion]</i>

875
01:06:55.579 --> 01:06:57.512
WHERE THE FUCK IS RED PLATOON?

876
01:06:57.581 --> 01:06:59.559
TELL THOSE ASSHOLES
TO GET UP HERE.

877
01:06:59.583 --> 01:07:02.394
ELIAS, WHAT THE FUCK ARE YOU DOING
BACK HERE? LISTEN TO ME, BARNES.

878
01:07:02.418 --> 01:07:04.853
THERE'S HOLES BACK HERE.

879
01:07:04.921 --> 01:07:06.855
THIRD PLATOON'S COMING
UP HERE. WE'RE HERE.

880
01:07:06.923 --> 01:07:09.858
DINKS GET MEN IN THESE HOLES,
THEY GOT US CAUGHT IN A CROSS FIRE.

881
01:07:09.926 --> 01:07:11.843
WE'LL SHOOT EACH OTHER TO SHIT.

882
01:07:11.911 --> 01:07:14.045
SOUNDS PRETTY
FAR OUT TO ME, ELIAS.

883
01:07:14.114 --> 01:07:16.480
I'VE SEEN IT HAPPEN.
YA TRANG IN '66.

884
01:07:16.549 --> 01:07:19.300
THEY CUT US TO FUCKING
PIECES. I NEED THREE MEN.

885
01:07:19.368 --> 01:07:21.886
OKAY, YOU GOT THEM. TAKE OFF.

886
01:07:21.955 --> 01:07:24.022
YOU KEEP POURING
OFF THAT COVER FIRE.

887
01:07:24.090 --> 01:07:27.324
I DON'T WANT TO BE STUCK OUT THERE
WITH MY ASS HANGING IN THE BREEZE.

888
01:07:27.393 --> 01:07:31.479
YOU DON'T TELL ME HOW
TO RUN MY WAR, ELIAS.

889
01:07:31.548 --> 01:07:35.049
NOW, YOU GO CRYING AND RAT-FUCKING
THE BRIGADE ON YOUR OWN TIME.

890
01:07:35.118 --> 01:07:38.419
BUT OUT HERE, YOU
BELONG TO ME. NOW MOVE.

891
01:07:38.488 --> 01:07:40.204
YOU'RE AN ASSHOLE, BARNES.

892
01:07:40.273 --> 01:07:42.251
<i>[Barnes] GET THAT
ASSHOLE O'NEILL UP HERE.</i>

893
01:07:42.275 --> 01:07:44.209
<i>[Explosion]</i>

894
01:07:44.277 --> 01:07:46.411
<i>[Radioman]...THIS IS TWO.
BE ADVISED WE'LL BE...</i>

895
01:07:47.631 --> 01:07:49.881
<i>[Gunshots]</i>

896
01:08:14.908 --> 01:08:16.908
[No Audible Dialogue]

897
01:08:23.617 --> 01:08:25.616
STAY DOWN!

898
01:08:39.599 --> 01:08:41.599
AMMO. AMMO.

899
01:08:45.605 --> 01:08:47.972
<i>[Shell Whistling]</i>

900
01:08:50.459 --> 01:08:52.510
<i>[Shell Whistling]</i>

901
01:08:53.529 --> 01:08:55.562
SARGE!

902
01:08:55.631 --> 01:08:57.765
SHORT ROUND!

903
01:08:57.834 --> 01:08:59.967
<i>[Shell Whistling]</i> FUCKING IDIOT!

904
01:09:02.472 --> 01:09:04.405
[Screaming] OH, GOD!

905
01:09:04.474 --> 01:09:06.474
<i>MEDIC! MEDIC!</i>

906
01:09:09.795 --> 01:09:11.896
<i>GET IT OFF OF YOU. MEDIC!</i>

907
01:09:12.966 --> 01:09:14.966
[Continues Screaming]

908
01:09:24.643 --> 01:09:26.911
AH!

909
01:09:26.980 --> 01:09:29.513
MEDIC! <i>[Shell Whistling]</i>

910
01:09:38.241 --> 01:09:39.773
<i>[Bunny] SATCHEL CHARGE!</i>

911
01:09:39.842 --> 01:09:42.343
[Screaming]

912
01:09:43.580 --> 01:09:46.096
DOC.

913
01:09:46.165 --> 01:09:48.032
DOC. HELP ME OUT. <i>OH, NO.</i>

914
01:09:48.100 --> 01:09:50.434
[Whimpering]

915
01:09:51.437 --> 01:09:53.437
JESUS.

916
01:09:55.441 --> 01:09:57.419
YOU OKAY? DON'T LEAVE ME, MAN.

917
01:09:57.443 --> 01:09:59.994
ALL RIGHT? DON'T LEAVE... ME.

918
01:10:00.063 --> 01:10:02.062
HEY, GATOR.

919
01:10:02.131 --> 01:10:04.465
YOU'LL BE OKAY, MAN.

920
01:10:04.533 --> 01:10:07.401
<i>GATOR, YOU'LL BE OKAY.</i>

921
01:10:07.470 --> 01:10:09.403
<i>[Doc] WAY TO GO, MAN.</i>
DROP YOUR RUCKS.

922
01:10:09.472 --> 01:10:12.034
<i>[Taylor] JUST HANG IN THERE.</i>
TAYLOR, YOU'RE COMING WITH US.

923
01:10:12.058 --> 01:10:14.859
<i>PLEASE, DON'T GO.</i>

924
01:10:14.927 --> 01:10:17.628
<i>YOU'RE GONNA BE OKAY.</i>

925
01:10:17.697 --> 01:10:20.248
<i>COME ON!</i> DOC, TAKE
CARE OF HIM, MAN.

926
01:10:20.316 --> 01:10:22.916
<i>[Shell Whistling]</i>

927
01:10:22.985 --> 01:10:26.921
<i>[Wolfe] REDLEG. REDLEG.
RIPPER, BRAVO TWO ACTUAL.</i>

928
01:10:26.990 --> 01:10:29.030
<i>ADJUSTMENT FOLLOWS. GRID...</i>

929
01:10:30.994 --> 01:10:33.427
YOU IGNORANT ASSHOLE!

930
01:10:33.496 --> 01:10:35.596
WHAT THE FUCK
COORDINATES ARE YOU GIVING?

931
01:10:35.665 --> 01:10:39.934
YOU WASTED A LOT OF PEOPLE UP
THERE WITH YOUR FUCKED-UP FIRE MISSION!

932
01:10:40.003 --> 01:10:42.436
YOU KNOW THAT?

933
01:10:42.488 --> 01:10:44.438
YOU KNOW THAT?

934
01:10:44.490 --> 01:10:46.773
AH, SHIT.

935
01:10:46.842 --> 01:10:50.244
REDLEG. REDLEG.
RIPPER, BRAVO TWO.

936
01:10:50.313 --> 01:10:53.347
CHECK YOUR FIRE.
CHECK YOUR FIRE.

937
01:11:03.776 --> 01:11:05.843
THEY'RE COMING.

938
01:11:08.715 --> 01:11:10.926
STAGGER YOURSELF
ACROSS THIS LINE.

939
01:11:10.950 --> 01:11:12.995
SHOOT ANYTHING THAT MOVES.

940
01:11:13.019 --> 01:11:15.870
THEY'LL BE COMING
FROM OVER THERE.

941
01:11:15.939 --> 01:11:19.259
ANY ONE OF THEM GETS
THROUGH, WE'RE TRULY FUCKED.

942
01:11:19.309 --> 01:11:21.229
WHERE IN THE HELL ARE YOU GOING?

943
01:11:22.295 --> 01:11:25.579
DOWN BY THE RIVER,
ABOUT A HUNDRED METERS,

944
01:11:25.648 --> 01:11:27.676
IN CASE THEY TRY TO FLANK US.

945
01:11:27.700 --> 01:11:30.613
<i>THIRD PLATOON IS COMING UP TO
OUR REAR, SO WATCH FOR THEM.</i>

946
01:11:30.637 --> 01:11:32.603
HEY, CAN I GO WITH YOU?

947
01:11:32.672 --> 01:11:34.605
NO.

948
01:11:34.674 --> 01:11:36.824
I MOVE FASTER ALONE.

949
01:11:39.895 --> 01:11:41.995
<i>[Explosion]</i>

950
01:11:43.166 --> 01:11:45.099
COME HERE.

951
01:11:45.168 --> 01:11:47.746
LET'S LET ARTY DO A
LITTLE BIT OF WORK HERE.

952
01:11:47.770 --> 01:11:50.582
YOU TELL EVERYBODY TO
PULL BACK TO THE CHURCH...

953
01:11:50.606 --> 01:11:52.584
AND LINK UP WITH THIRD PLATOON.

954
01:11:52.608 --> 01:11:54.587
YOU GOT THAT? GOT IT.

955
01:11:54.611 --> 01:11:57.712
WHAT ABOUT ELIAS? IF WE
PULL BACK, HE'LL BE CUT OFF.

956
01:11:57.780 --> 01:12:00.381
YOU JUST HAUL ASS
TOO, LIEUTENANT.

957
01:12:00.450 --> 01:12:02.383
<i>[Explosion]</i> I'LL GET HIM.

958
01:12:02.452 --> 01:12:05.503
<i>TWO ALPHA. TWO CHARLIE.</i>

959
01:12:26.292 --> 01:12:28.393
[No Audible Dialogue]

960
01:12:29.963 --> 01:12:32.396
<i>[Machine Gun Firing]</i>

961
01:12:41.240 --> 01:12:44.041
I GOT TWO OF THEM FUCKERS, MAN.

962
01:12:44.109 --> 01:12:48.028
- I GOT ONE.
- HO CHI MINH
SUCKS DEAD DICKS!

963
01:12:48.097 --> 01:12:50.030
[Growling]

964
01:12:50.099 --> 01:12:52.099
CRAWFORD.

965
01:12:53.686 --> 01:12:55.636
OH, MAN.

966
01:12:55.705 --> 01:12:59.023
KISS MY ASS, MAN. I
NEVER THOUGHT I'D GET HIT.

967
01:12:59.091 --> 01:13:02.894
IT'S A LUNG, BABE. YOU
GOT TWO OF THEM FUCKERS.

968
01:13:02.962 --> 01:13:05.557
- WHERE'S ELIAS?
- SARGE, THERE'S A BUNCH
OF GOOKS CAME THROUGH THERE.

969
01:13:05.581 --> 01:13:07.498
WE GOT THREE OF THEM FUCKERS.

970
01:13:07.567 --> 01:13:10.368
HEY. DID YOU HEAR THE ARTY
SHIFT? WE'RE PULLING BACK.

971
01:13:10.436 --> 01:13:12.676
NOW GET YOUR WOUNDED MAN
AND GET THE FUCK BACK TO CHURCH.

972
01:13:12.738 --> 01:13:14.867
<i>GET GOING.</i> BUT ELIAS IS
STILL OUT THERE, SARGE.

973
01:13:14.891 --> 01:13:16.852
<i>TAYLOR, I'LL GET HIM.</i>

974
01:13:16.876 --> 01:13:19.204
YOU GET CRAWFORD IN. NOW, BEFORE
YOU ARTICLE 15 BOTH YOUR ASSES.

975
01:13:19.228 --> 01:13:21.162
MOVE!

976
01:13:21.230 --> 01:13:23.297
COME ON. MOVE IT.

977
01:13:51.760 --> 01:13:53.760
[Speaking Vietnamese]

978
01:14:25.294 --> 01:14:28.128
[Speaking Vietnamese]

979
01:14:32.301 --> 01:14:34.285
<i>[Gunshots]</i>

980
01:14:36.355 --> 01:14:38.455
<i>[Gunshots]</i>

981
01:14:40.626 --> 01:14:42.643
<i>[Gunshots]</i>

982
01:14:49.035 --> 01:14:51.435
<i>[Gunfire]</i>

983
01:14:51.504 --> 01:14:54.288
[Shouting]

984
01:14:54.340 --> 01:14:57.174
<i>[Gunshots]</i>

985
01:15:17.580 --> 01:15:20.047
WE STILL GOT YOU.
COME ON, BROTHER.

986
01:15:20.115 --> 01:15:23.551
<i>[Man] MEDIC, WHERE THE
FUCK ARE YOU? KEG IT, MAN.</i>

987
01:15:23.619 --> 01:15:27.555
<i>OH, YEAH. YOU GOT IT. YOU'RE GONNA
BE ALL RIGHT IN A MINUTE, BROTHER.</i>

988
01:15:27.623 --> 01:15:29.557
OKAY, HOLD ON.

989
01:15:29.625 --> 01:15:32.393
<i>TAYLOR, WHERE ARE YOU GOING?</i>

990
01:15:37.300 --> 01:15:39.300
<i>[Rustling]</i>

991
01:16:41.447 --> 01:16:43.297
ELIAS IS DEAD.

992
01:16:43.366 --> 01:16:45.344
FALL BACK WITH THE PLATOON.

993
01:16:45.368 --> 01:16:48.052
<i>GET GOING.</i> HE'S DEAD?

994
01:16:48.121 --> 01:16:51.155
YEAH. YEAH, HE'S BACK THERE
ABOUT A HUNDRED METERS.

995
01:16:51.223 --> 01:16:53.240
YOU SAW HIM? WHERE?

996
01:16:53.309 --> 01:16:55.421
HE'S DEAD. THERE'S GOOKS
ALL OVER THE GODDAMN PLACE.

997
01:16:55.445 --> 01:16:57.495
GET MOVING.

998
01:17:11.610 --> 01:17:14.128
LET'S GO. LET'S GO. LET'S
GO. COME ON. MOVE IT.

999
01:17:50.716 --> 01:17:52.745
LET'S GO. LET'S GO.
MOVE IT. MOVE IT.

1000
01:17:52.769 --> 01:17:54.768
<i>OKAY, LET'S GO.</i>

1001
01:18:16.959 --> 01:18:19.877
YOU OKAY, HAROLD?
YOU'RE ON THE NEXT ONE.

1002
01:18:19.945 --> 01:18:22.746
YOU'RE OKAY, BUD.

1003
01:18:52.144 --> 01:18:54.144
[No Audible Dialogue]

1004
01:19:06.825 --> 01:19:08.943
OH, FUCK!

1005
01:19:11.814 --> 01:19:13.747
THEY'VE GOT ELIAS.

1006
01:19:13.816 --> 01:19:15.949
WHAT?

1007
01:19:21.623 --> 01:19:23.858
BACK DOWN. BACK DOWN THERE.

1008
01:19:30.183 --> 01:19:32.116
<i>[Pilot On Radio] SNAKE
ONE-NINER, FLY FOUR.</i>

1009
01:19:32.185 --> 01:19:34.529
<i>THERE'S STILL ONE ON THE DECK
DOWN THERE. BRING IN THE GUNSHIPS.</i>

1010
01:19:34.553 --> 01:19:36.686
<i>[Radio Continues, Indistinct]</i>

1011
01:19:39.025 --> 01:19:41.025
<i>[Machine Gun Firing]</i>

1012
01:19:58.161 --> 01:20:01.145
<i>[Pilot] HOLD YOUR ARMOR.
GUNS, GUNS. PULL OFF.</i>

1013
01:20:01.214 --> 01:20:03.213
<i>WE'RE TRYING TO
COME AROUND MY SIDE.</i>

1014
01:20:59.638 --> 01:21:01.738
HE KILLED HIM.

1015
01:21:01.807 --> 01:21:05.242
I KNOW THAT HE KILLED HIM. I SAW
HIS EYES WHEN HE CAME BACK IN.

1016
01:21:05.311 --> 01:21:07.244
HOW DO YOU KNOW THE
DINKS DIDN'T GET HIM?

1017
01:21:07.313 --> 01:21:09.246
YOU GOT NO PROOF.

1018
01:21:09.315 --> 01:21:11.626
PROOF'S IN THE EYES.
WHEN YOU KNOW, YOU KNOW.

1019
01:21:11.650 --> 01:21:13.795
YOU WERE THERE, RHAH. I
KNOW WHAT YOU WERE THINKING.

1020
01:21:13.819 --> 01:21:15.930
I SAY WE FRAG THAT
FUCKER TONIGHT.

1021
01:21:15.954 --> 01:21:18.155
I GO WITH THAT.
AN EYE FOR AN EYE.

1022
01:21:18.224 --> 01:21:21.508
I SAY LET MILITARY
JUSTICE DO THE JOB ON HIM.

1023
01:21:22.494 --> 01:21:24.428
COME ON. FUCK THE
MILITARY JUSTICE!

1024
01:21:24.496 --> 01:21:26.430
ARE YOU JOKING ME?

1025
01:21:26.498 --> 01:21:28.476
WHOSE STORY DO YOU THINK
THEY'RE GONNA BELIEVE? O'NEILL'S?

1026
01:21:28.500 --> 01:21:30.434
BUNNY'S? WOLFE'S? BULLSHIT!

1027
01:21:30.502 --> 01:21:34.905
<i>YOU TRY THAT, AND BARNES WILL SHOVE IT
RIGHT BACK UP YOUR ASS WITH A CANDLE ON IT.</i>

1028
01:21:34.973 --> 01:21:36.907
THEN WHAT DO YOU SUGGEST WE DO?

1029
01:21:36.975 --> 01:21:39.443
I SUGGEST, YOU ALL
WATCH YOUR OWN ASSES.

1030
01:21:39.511 --> 01:21:41.678
'CAUSE BARNES IS GONNA BE
COMING DOWN ON ALL OF THEM.

1031
01:21:41.747 --> 01:21:43.680
<i>YOU JUST GONNA
FORGET ABOUT ELIAS...</i>

1032
01:21:43.749 --> 01:21:45.749
AND ALL THE GOOD TIMES
WE DONE HAD RIGHT IN HERE?

1033
01:21:45.818 --> 01:21:49.019
<i>SHIT, YOU'RE TRYING TO CURE THE
HEADACHE BY CUTTING OFF THE HEAD.</i>

1034
01:21:49.088 --> 01:21:53.741
ELIAS DIDN'T ASK YOU TO
FIGHT HIS BATTLES FOR HIM.

1035
01:21:53.809 --> 01:21:57.745
AND IF THERE'S A HEAVEN...
AND GOD I HOPE THERE IS...

1036
01:21:57.813 --> 01:22:03.250
I KNOW HE'S SITTING UP THERE DRUNK
AS A FUCKING MONKEY AND SMOKING SHIT,

1037
01:22:03.318 --> 01:22:05.819
'CAUSE HE DONE LEFT
HIS PAINS DOWN HERE.

1038
01:22:05.888 --> 01:22:10.156
YOU'RE WRONG, MAN. ANY WAY YOU
CUT IT, BARNES IS A FUCKING MURDERER!

1039
01:22:10.225 --> 01:22:12.242
TAYLOR,

1040
01:22:12.311 --> 01:22:14.744
I REMEMBER WHEN
YOU FIRST CAME IN HERE,

1041
01:22:14.813 --> 01:22:16.958
TELLING ME HOW MUCH
YOU ADMIRED THE BASTARD.

1042
01:22:16.982 --> 01:22:18.915
I WAS WRONG. WRONG?

1043
01:22:18.984 --> 01:22:22.297
YOU AIN'T NEVER BEEN
RIGHT ABOUT NOTHIN'!

1044
01:22:22.321 --> 01:22:24.821
DIG THIS, YOU ASSHOLES,
AND DIG IT GOOD.

1045
01:22:26.158 --> 01:22:29.304
BARNES HAS BEEN SHOT
SEVEN TIMES, AND HE AIN'T DEAD.

1046
01:22:29.328 --> 01:22:32.140
DOES THAT MEAN
ANYTHING TO YOU? HUH?

1047
01:22:32.164 --> 01:22:34.931
BARNES AIN'T MEANT TO DIE.

1048
01:22:35.000 --> 01:22:36.978
THE ONLY THING THAT
COULD KILL BARNES...

1049
01:22:37.002 --> 01:22:39.102
IS BARNES.

1050
01:22:39.171 --> 01:22:41.905
<i>[Barnes] YOU TALKING
ABOUT KILLING?</i>

1051
01:22:49.948 --> 01:22:51.948
HMM?

1052
01:22:53.952 --> 01:22:55.952
Y'ALL EXPERTS?

1053
01:22:57.790 --> 01:23:00.071
Y'ALL KNOW ABOUT KILLING?

1054
01:23:01.026 --> 01:23:04.595
I'D LIKE TO HEAR
ABOUT IT, POTHEADS.

1055
01:23:11.153 --> 01:23:14.488
ARE YOU SMOKING THIS SHIT
SO'S TO ESCAPE FROM REALITY?

1056
01:23:16.292 --> 01:23:19.142
ME, I DON'T NEED THIS SHIT.

1057
01:23:25.484 --> 01:23:28.985
I AM REALITY.

1058
01:23:33.742 --> 01:23:35.720
THERE'S THE WAY IT OUGHT TO BE,

1059
01:23:35.744 --> 01:23:38.011
AND THERE'S THE WAY IT IS.

1060
01:23:41.349 --> 01:23:44.951
ELIAS WAS FULL OF SHIT.

1061
01:23:45.020 --> 01:23:48.055
ELIAS WAS A CRUSADER.

1062
01:23:48.123 --> 01:23:50.057
NOW, I GOT NO FIGHT...

1063
01:23:50.125 --> 01:23:52.726
WITH ANY MAN WHO
DOES WHAT HE'S TOLD.

1064
01:23:52.795 --> 01:23:54.728
BUT WHEN HE DON'T,

1065
01:23:54.797 --> 01:23:57.064
THE MACHINE BREAKS DOWN.

1066
01:23:57.132 --> 01:23:59.566
AND WHEN THE
MACHINE BREAKS DOWN,

1067
01:23:59.634 --> 01:24:01.802
WE BREAK DOWN.

1068
01:24:02.805 --> 01:24:05.572
AND I AIN'T GONNA ALLOW THAT...

1069
01:24:05.640 --> 01:24:07.908
IN ANY OF YOU.

1070
01:24:07.976 --> 01:24:10.076
NOT ONE.

1071
01:24:17.820 --> 01:24:19.820
<i>[Spits]</i>

1072
01:24:26.328 --> 01:24:28.494
Y'ALL LOVE ELIAS.

1073
01:24:33.168 --> 01:24:35.501
OH, YOU WANNA KICK ASS.

1074
01:24:37.339 --> 01:24:39.339
YEAH.

1075
01:24:41.343 --> 01:24:44.845
WELL, HERE I AM,
ALL BY MY LONESOME.

1076
01:24:47.950 --> 01:24:50.951
AND THERE AIN'T
NOBODY GONNA KNOW.

1077
01:24:55.958 --> 01:24:58.959
SIX OF YOU BOYS AGAINST ME.

1078
01:25:04.299 --> 01:25:06.833
KILL ME.

1079
01:25:16.361 --> 01:25:18.461
HUH.

1080
01:25:23.802 --> 01:25:25.802
I SHIT ON ALL OF YOU.

1081
01:25:27.839 --> 01:25:30.740
YOU MOTHERFUCKER!

1082
01:25:32.094 --> 01:25:34.144
<i>[All Shouting, Indistinct]</i>

1083
01:25:36.314 --> 01:25:38.932
<i>COME ON, MAN. GO.</i> GET HIM!

1084
01:25:39.001 --> 01:25:42.219
<i>GET HIM, CHRIS.</i>

1085
01:25:44.523 --> 01:25:47.141
EASY, BARNES. DON'T DO IT, MAN.

1086
01:25:47.209 --> 01:25:49.109
<i>[Rhah] YOU'LL GO
DINKY DAU IN L.B.J., MAN.</i>

1087
01:25:49.177 --> 01:25:51.878
TEN YEARS FOR KILLING
AN ENLISTED MAN.

1088
01:25:51.947 --> 01:25:55.115
TEN YEARS. YOU'LL CLIMB
THE FUCKING WALLS, MAN.

1089
01:25:57.436 --> 01:25:59.436
<i>DON'T DO IT.</i>

1090
01:26:09.781 --> 01:26:11.781
[Grunts]

1091
01:26:17.122 --> 01:26:19.222
DEATH?

1092
01:26:19.291 --> 01:26:22.292
WHAT DO YOU ALL
KNOW ABOUT DEATH?

1093
01:26:36.475 --> 01:26:38.453
<i>[Taylor] THEY SENT US BACK
INTO THE VALLEY THE NEXT DAY,</i>

1094
01:26:38.477 --> 01:26:42.812
<i>ABOUT 2,000 METERS FROM
CAMBODIA, INTO A BATTALION PERIMETER.</i>

1095
01:26:42.881 --> 01:26:46.666
<i>IT FELT LIKE WE WERE RETURNING
TO THE SCENE OF A CRIME.</i>

1096
01:27:20.586 --> 01:27:24.905
<i>ALPHA COMPANY HAD BEEN HIT HARD
THE DAY BEFORE BY A SIZEABLE FORCE,</i>

1097
01:27:24.974 --> 01:27:27.307
<i>AND CHARLIE COMPANY HAD
BEEN PROBED THAT NIGHT.</i>

1098
01:27:27.376 --> 01:27:30.577
<i>THERE WERE OTHER BATTALIONS IN THE
VALLEY... WE WEREN'T THE ONLY ONES...</i>

1099
01:27:30.645 --> 01:27:33.096
<i>BUT WE KNEW WE WERE GOING
TO BE THE BAIT TO LURE THEM OUT.</i>

1100
01:27:33.164 --> 01:27:37.717
<i>SOMEWHERE OUT THERE WAS
THE ENTIRE 141st N.V.A. REGIMENT.</i>

1101
01:27:45.844 --> 01:27:48.512
[No Audible Dialogue]

1102
01:27:55.938 --> 01:28:00.357
<i>CAUGHT THOSE MOTHERFUCKERS TRYING TO PULL
SOME SHIT ON CHARLIE COMPANY LAST NIGHT.</i>

1103
01:28:00.426 --> 01:28:03.026
THEY FOUND MAPS ON THEM, MAN.

1104
01:28:03.094 --> 01:28:05.072
GOT A FRIEND AT BATTALION.

1105
01:28:05.096 --> 01:28:07.909
SAYS THEY HAD EVERY
FUCKING FOXHOLE HERE FIXED ON.

1106
01:28:07.933 --> 01:28:12.636
DISTANCES, TREE LINES,
OUR CLAYMORES, EVERYTHING.

1107
01:28:12.704 --> 01:28:14.704
THIS IS BAD, MAN.

1108
01:28:14.773 --> 01:28:16.806
I GOT BAD VIBES HERE.

1109
01:28:16.875 --> 01:28:19.521
I ALSO HEARD WE'RE IN
FUCKING CAMBODIA RIGHT NOW.

1110
01:28:19.545 --> 01:28:22.345
CAMBODIA? MAN,
YOU'RE KIDDING ME.

1111
01:28:22.413 --> 01:28:24.947
YOU WANTED TO SEE ME, SIR?

1112
01:28:26.284 --> 01:28:28.217
YEAH, RAMUCCI.

1113
01:28:28.286 --> 01:28:31.220
LOOKS LIKE YOU GOT ELIAS'S
SQUAD NOW. SQUAD, SIR?

1114
01:28:31.289 --> 01:28:34.101
I DIDN'T KNOW WE WERE STILL REFERRING
TO THIS PLATOON IN TERMS OF SQUADS.

1115
01:28:34.125 --> 01:28:36.604
ALL RIGHT. LOOK. I WANT YOU
TO TAKE THOSE TWO HOLES.

1116
01:28:36.628 --> 01:28:38.706
RIGHT THERE AND THERE.

1117
01:28:38.730 --> 01:28:41.826
YOU'RE TYING IT OFF WITH
BARNES UP HERE, KING DOWN THERE.

1118
01:28:41.850 --> 01:28:44.251
YEAH. BEGGING YOUR PARDON, SIR,

1119
01:28:44.319 --> 01:28:46.253
MY TWO HOLES ARE
FAR ENOUGH APART...

1120
01:28:46.321 --> 01:28:48.922
YOU CAN RUN A REGIMENT
THROUGH THEM AND NEVER SEE IT.

1121
01:28:48.991 --> 01:28:51.024
I GOT FIVE LIVE
BODIES LEFT, SIR.

1122
01:28:51.093 --> 01:28:53.054
LOOK, I DON'T WANT TO HEAR
YOUR PROBLEMS, RAMUCCI.

1123
01:28:53.078 --> 01:28:55.011
YOU'LL GET NEW MEN ANY DAY.

1124
01:28:55.080 --> 01:28:56.891
MEANTIME, YOU MAKE
DO LIKE EVERYBODY ELSE.

1125
01:28:56.915 --> 01:28:59.311
I DIDN'T ASK FOR THIS JOB.
I DON'T WANT TO HEAR IT.

1126
01:28:59.335 --> 01:29:02.269
- OH, YOU DON'T WANT TO HEAR IT.
- YEAH, THAT'S RIGHT.

1127
01:29:02.338 --> 01:29:05.939
I DON'T WANT TO HEAR IT, 'CAUSE TO TELL
YOU THE TRUTH, I DON'T GIVE A SHIT, OKAY?

1128
01:29:06.008 --> 01:29:08.024
I JUST DON'T GIVE A
FLYING FUCK ANYMORE.

1129
01:29:08.093 --> 01:29:10.160
RIGHT.

1130
01:29:15.701 --> 01:29:18.852
I'M GLAD I AIN'T
GOING WITH THEM.

1131
01:29:20.522 --> 01:29:24.073
SOMEWHERE OUT THERE IS THE
BEAST, AND HE HUNGRY TONIGHT.

1132
01:29:24.142 --> 01:29:26.242
MOTHERFUCKIN' BUMMER.

1133
01:29:26.311 --> 01:29:30.313
TEN DAYS AND A WAKE-UP, AND
I'M STILL DEALING WITH THIS SHIT.

1134
01:29:34.202 --> 01:29:36.180
WHAT'S THE MATTER WITH YOU, MAN?

1135
01:29:36.204 --> 01:29:38.538
HOW COME YOU AIN'T
WRITING NOBODY?

1136
01:29:38.606 --> 01:29:41.141
WHAT ABOUT YOUR FOLKS?

1137
01:29:41.209 --> 01:29:43.810
THAT GRANDMA YOU
WAS TELLING ME ABOUT?

1138
01:29:45.530 --> 01:29:47.464
<i>GIRL?</i>

1139
01:29:50.135 --> 01:29:54.087
YOU GOT A MOTHER AND FATHER,
DON'T YOU? THERE MUST BE SOMEBODY.

1140
01:29:54.156 --> 01:29:56.689
NAH, THERE'S NOBODY.

1141
01:29:57.976 --> 01:30:00.977
YOU'VE BEEN SMOKING TOO
MUCH OF THIS SHIT, TROOP.

1142
01:30:02.480 --> 01:30:06.082
GOTTA CONTROL THAT.
BRING A MAN DOWN.

1143
01:30:06.151 --> 01:30:08.796
I REMEMBER WHEN YOU FIRST
COME OUT HERE TO THE BUSH.

1144
01:30:08.820 --> 01:30:11.471
YOU WERE AS GREEN
AS A... [Laughing]

1145
01:30:11.540 --> 01:30:16.092
DID YOU EVER GET CAUGHT IN A MISTAKE
THAT YOU JUST CAN'T GET OUT OF, KING?

1146
01:30:16.160 --> 01:30:18.239
THERE'S A WAY OUT
OF ANYTHING, MAN.

1147
01:30:18.263 --> 01:30:21.781
JUST KEEP YOUR PECKER
HARD AND YOUR POWDER DRY,

1148
01:30:21.850 --> 01:30:24.851
AND THE WORM WILL TURN.

1149
01:30:26.855 --> 01:30:29.122
HOW MANY DAYS YOU SHORT?

1150
01:30:29.191 --> 01:30:31.240
NAH, IT'S NOT JUST ME.

1151
01:30:31.309 --> 01:30:33.460
IT'S THE WAY THE
WHOLE THING WORKS.

1152
01:30:33.528 --> 01:30:35.462
PEOPLE LIKE ELIAS GET WASTED.

1153
01:30:35.530 --> 01:30:39.299
PEOPLE LIKE BARNES JUST GO ON
MAKING UP THE RULES ANY WAY THEY WANT.

1154
01:30:39.368 --> 01:30:41.301
SO WHAT DO WE DO?

1155
01:30:41.370 --> 01:30:44.137
SIT IN THE MIDDLE
AND SUCK ON IT.

1156
01:30:44.205 --> 01:30:46.790
WE JUST DON'T
ADD UP TO DRY SHIT.

1157
01:30:46.859 --> 01:30:48.891
WHOEVER SAID WE DID, MAN?

1158
01:30:48.960 --> 01:30:51.728
ALL YOU GOT TO DO IS
MAKE IT OUT OF HERE,

1159
01:30:51.797 --> 01:30:53.730
AND IT'S ALL GRAVY.

1160
01:30:53.799 --> 01:30:56.466
EVERY DAY, THE REST
OF YOUR LIFE... GRAVY.

1161
01:30:59.638 --> 01:31:02.739
OH, SHIT. SUPER-LIFER.

1162
01:31:02.808 --> 01:31:06.192
HEY KING, COLLECT UP YOUR SHIT.
YOUR ORDERS JUST COME THROUGH.

1163
01:31:06.261 --> 01:31:07.889
OH, LOOK, MAN.
DON'T FUCK WITH ME.

1164
01:31:07.913 --> 01:31:10.458
WHAT DO YOU NEED, A WRITTEN
INVITATION, FOR CHRISSAKE?

1165
01:31:10.482 --> 01:31:13.250
COCKSUCKER! OH, WOW!

1166
01:31:13.318 --> 01:31:15.418
THE LIFERS DONE MADE A MISTAKE.

1167
01:31:15.487 --> 01:31:17.420
THEY CUT ME SOME SLACK, TAYLOR.

1168
01:31:17.489 --> 01:31:19.267
GET YOUR PIG TO
RODRIGUEZ. YOU GOT TEN

1169
01:31:19.291 --> 01:31:21.424
MINUTES TO MAKE THE
LAST CHOPPER OUT OF HERE.

1170
01:31:21.493 --> 01:31:23.471
'CAUSE IF YOU'RE NOT ON IT,

1171
01:31:23.495 --> 01:31:26.096
I'M GONNA BE.

1172
01:31:26.164 --> 01:31:28.142
TAYLOR, FRANCIS IS COMING UP.

1173
01:31:28.166 --> 01:31:30.166
<i>THAT'S GREAT KING.
I'M HAPPY FOR YOU, MAN.</i>

1174
01:31:30.235 --> 01:31:32.435
TAKE IT ON HOME
FOR ME, OKAY? YEAH.

1175
01:31:32.504 --> 01:31:35.321
YOU GOT MY ADDRESS. YOU KNOW
WHERE YOU CAN GET A HOLD OF ME.

1176
01:31:35.390 --> 01:31:39.325
[Chuckling] I GOTTA DI DI, MAN. I
DON'T WANNA MISS THAT CHOPPER.

1177
01:31:39.394 --> 01:31:42.629
WHEW.

1178
01:31:42.698 --> 01:31:44.698
YOU OKAY? YEAH, I'M OKAY.

1179
01:31:45.701 --> 01:31:47.728
REMEMBER NOW, TAKE IT EASY.

1180
01:31:47.752 --> 01:31:50.553
DON'T THINK TOO MUCH,
AND DON'T YOU BE NO FOOL.

1181
01:31:50.622 --> 01:31:52.600
REMEMBER, AIN'T NO SUCH
THING AS A COWARD OUT HERE.

1182
01:31:52.624 --> 01:31:55.057
DON'T MEAN NOTHIN'.

1183
01:31:55.126 --> 01:31:57.126
MY MAN.

1184
01:32:03.735 --> 01:32:05.818
I'LL WALK YOU OUT, MAN.

1185
01:32:10.325 --> 01:32:12.258
<i>[Francis] TAKE IT EASY, KING.</i>

1186
01:32:12.327 --> 01:32:16.095
I'M GONNA TAKE IT ANY WAY I CAN
GET IT, BROTHER. I HEAR YOU. LATER.

1187
01:32:16.164 --> 01:32:19.248
MY FOOT IS FUCKED-UP, SARGE.
NO, MAN! DON'T TOUCH THIS!

1188
01:32:19.317 --> 01:32:21.751
<i>I'VE GOTTA GET ON
THE CHOPPER, MAN.</i>

1189
01:32:21.819 --> 01:32:24.799
SO WHAT'S THE PROBLEM?
SAYS HE CAN'T WALK.

1190
01:32:24.823 --> 01:32:27.757
SHIT.

1191
01:32:27.826 --> 01:32:31.494
MARTIN, GET YOUR BOOTS ON.

1192
01:32:33.832 --> 01:32:35.810
AND THE NEXT TIME I CATCH YOU...

1193
01:32:35.834 --> 01:32:38.768
SPRAYING SKEETER REPELLENT
ON YOUR FUCKING FEET,

1194
01:32:38.837 --> 01:32:41.937
I'M GONNA COURT-MARTIAL
YOUR NIGGER ASS.

1195
01:32:42.006 --> 01:32:44.440
WELL, THEN COURT-MARTIAL
ME, MOTHERFUCKER!

1196
01:32:44.509 --> 01:32:47.293
BUST MY ASS! SEND ME
TO FUCKING LONG BINH!

1197
01:32:47.362 --> 01:32:49.412
<i>YOU CAN DO YOUR FUCKING WORST!</i>

1198
01:32:49.481 --> 01:32:52.916
YOU WHITE FOLKS HAVE GOT
YOUR LAST CLICK OUT OF JUNIOR!

1199
01:32:52.984 --> 01:32:56.569
O'NEILL, GET ME THAT CENTIPEDE.

1200
01:32:56.638 --> 01:32:58.805
SERGEANT? <i>YEAH.</i>

1201
01:32:58.874 --> 01:33:03.793
THAT LONG, HAIRY, RED AND BLACK
BASTARD I FOUND IN THE AMMO CRATE.

1202
01:33:03.862 --> 01:33:07.563
<i>I'M GONNA PUT IT IN THIS BOY'S
CROTCH, SEE IF HE CAN WALK.</i>

1203
01:33:07.632 --> 01:33:09.899
I REMEMBER NOW.

1204
01:33:09.968 --> 01:33:12.068
HEY! NOW HOLD UP, MAN.

1205
01:33:12.137 --> 01:33:14.070
YOU JUST HOLD UP
AND WAIT, ALL RIGHT?

1206
01:33:14.139 --> 01:33:17.106
FUCK IT. I'LL WALK. I'LL
FUCKING WALK, MAN!

1207
01:33:17.175 --> 01:33:20.043
FUCKING PUSSY, MAN. HEY, SARGE,
I GOTTA HAVE HIM IN MY HOLE?

1208
01:33:20.112 --> 01:33:22.429
YEAH. UH, BOB?

1209
01:33:22.497 --> 01:33:24.564
I'D LIKE TO SPEAK
TO YOU A MINUTE.

1210
01:33:28.987 --> 01:33:31.988
I CAN'T TAKE IT NO MORE.

1211
01:33:32.056 --> 01:33:34.090
<i>[Junior] I CAN'T TAKE IT
ANY MORE. BOB. BOB.</i>

1212
01:33:34.159 --> 01:33:36.092
YEAH. WHAT IS IT?

1213
01:33:36.161 --> 01:33:39.307
BOB, I GOT ELIAS'S R &
R. IT'S IN THREE DAYS.

1214
01:33:39.331 --> 01:33:42.765
I WAS THINKING ABOUT GOING
TO HAWAII AND SEE PATSY.

1215
01:33:42.834 --> 01:33:45.646
HEY, BOB, COME ON. I NEVER
ASKED YOU FOR A FUCKING THING.

1216
01:33:45.670 --> 01:33:47.581
I WAS THINKING, MAYBE...
WELL, TO BE HONEST WITH YOU,

1217
01:33:47.605 --> 01:33:49.583
I WAS HOPING YOU'D PUT ME
ON THAT CHOPPER WITH KING.

1218
01:33:49.607 --> 01:33:51.585
WHAT DO YOU SAY
THERE, CHIEF-A-ROONEY?

1219
01:33:51.609 --> 01:33:53.543
NAH, I CAN'T DO
THAT FOR YOU, RED.

1220
01:33:53.611 --> 01:33:55.711
WE NEED EVERY
SWINGING DICK IN THE FIELD.

1221
01:33:55.780 --> 01:33:57.758
<i>HEY BOB. TALK TO ME FOR
CHRISSAKE.</i> SIN LOY, BUDDY.

1222
01:33:57.782 --> 01:33:59.927
<i>ALL I'M ASKING YOU FOR IS
THREE FUCKING DAYS HERE.</i>

1223
01:33:59.951 --> 01:34:02.685
I AM TALKING TO YOU, RED,
AND I'M TELLING YOU "NO."

1224
01:34:02.754 --> 01:34:05.722
SO GET BACK IN YOUR FOXHOLE.

1225
01:34:05.790 --> 01:34:09.558
BOB, I GOT A BAD FEELING
ON THIS ONE, ALL RIGHT?

1226
01:34:09.627 --> 01:34:12.561
I MEAN I GOT A BAD FEELING.

1227
01:34:12.630 --> 01:34:15.398
I DON'T THINK I'M GONNA
MAKE IT OUT OF HERE.

1228
01:34:15.466 --> 01:34:17.967
DO YOU UNDERSTAND
WHAT I'M SAYING TO YOU?

1229
01:34:18.036 --> 01:34:21.654
EVERYBODY GOT TO
DIE SOMETIME, RED.

1230
01:34:29.331 --> 01:34:31.598
OH, SHIT.

1231
01:34:43.961 --> 01:34:48.448
GOOD-BYE, MOTHERFUCKERS!

1232
01:34:56.307 --> 01:34:59.742
<i>[Explosion, Machine Gun Firing]</i>

1233
01:34:59.810 --> 01:35:02.544
THAT'S THE FUCKING AMBUSH.

1234
01:35:02.613 --> 01:35:04.881
THEY AIN'T WAITING TILL LATER.

1235
01:35:04.949 --> 01:35:07.383
IT'S FUCKING COMING NOW, MAN.

1236
01:35:07.451 --> 01:35:09.886
RIGHT FUCKING NOW.

1237
01:35:09.955 --> 01:35:13.222
<i>[Gunshots]</i>

1238
01:35:13.291 --> 01:35:15.258
<i>YOU KNOW, JUNIOR.</i>

1239
01:35:15.326 --> 01:35:18.227
SOME OF THE THINGS
WE DONE, MAN...

1240
01:35:18.296 --> 01:35:21.264
I DON'T FEEL LIKE WE
DONE SOMETHING WRONG.

1241
01:35:21.332 --> 01:35:24.733
SOMETIMES, MAN,

1242
01:35:24.803 --> 01:35:27.136
I GET THIS BAD FEELING.

1243
01:35:30.308 --> 01:35:32.592
<i>I TOLD THE PADRE THE
TRUTH. I LIKE IT HERE.</i>

1244
01:35:32.661 --> 01:35:35.762
YOU GET TO DO WHAT YOU
WANT. NOBODY FUCKS WITH YOU.

1245
01:35:35.830 --> 01:35:38.431
THE ONLY WORRY YOU GOT IS DYING.

1246
01:35:38.499 --> 01:35:41.100
AND IF THAT HAPPENS, YOU
WON'T KNOW ABOUT IT, ANYWAY.

1247
01:35:41.169 --> 01:35:43.236
SO WHAT THE FUCK, MAN?

1248
01:35:43.304 --> 01:35:47.207
SHIT. I GOTTA BE IN THIS
HOLE WITH YOU, MAN?

1249
01:35:47.275 --> 01:35:49.776
I JUST KNOW I
SHOULDN'T HAVE COME.

1250
01:35:50.779 --> 01:35:52.795
<i>DON'T YOU WORRY, JUNIOR.</i>

1251
01:35:52.864 --> 01:35:55.764
YOU'RE HANGING WITH
AUDIE MURPHY HERE, MY MAN.

1252
01:35:58.169 --> 01:36:01.537
BRAVO THREE. BRAVO THREE,
BRAVO SIX. SEND ME A GRID. OVER.

1253
01:36:01.606 --> 01:36:04.907
I CAN'T SIR. WE'RE PINNED DOWN.
THEY'RE IN THE FUCKING TREES.

1254
01:36:04.976 --> 01:36:07.059
OKAY, THREE ALPHA.
NOW, CALM DOWN, SON.

1255
01:36:07.128 --> 01:36:10.229
I'LL GET YOU A FIRE MISSION
ASAP. SMOKE WILL BE FIRST.

1256
01:36:10.298 --> 01:36:13.900
LIEUTENANT'S DEAD. RADIOMAN LOOKS
DEAD, SIR. I DON'T KNOW WHERE THE MAP IS.

1257
01:36:13.968 --> 01:36:16.113
THEY'RE ALL AROUND US, SIR.
MOVING IN... HUNDREDS OF THEM.

1258
01:36:16.137 --> 01:36:18.404
I CAN HEAR THEM TALKING GOOK.

1259
01:36:18.473 --> 01:36:21.407
OKAY, THREE ALPHA. NOW SPOT THAT
SMOKE AND TELL ME WHERE TO SHIFT.

1260
01:36:21.476 --> 01:36:24.243
JUST CALM DOWN, SON. HANG
IN THERE. WE'LL GET YOU OUT.

1261
01:36:24.312 --> 01:36:26.362
JUST TELL ME WHERE
THE ROUNDS HIT. OVER.

1262
01:36:27.465 --> 01:36:29.465
<i>[Shell Whistling]</i>

1263
01:36:43.181 --> 01:36:45.643
THREE ALPHA, SIX. HOW
ABOUT THOSE ROUNDS, SON?

1264
01:36:45.667 --> 01:36:47.600
CAN YOU ADJUST FIRE? OVER.

1265
01:36:51.439 --> 01:36:56.442
THREE ALPHA, SIX. IF YOU CAN'T TALK,
SON, JUST KEY YOUR HANDSET TWICE. OVER.

1266
01:37:00.615 --> 01:37:03.716
[Gunfire On Radio]

1267
01:37:03.785 --> 01:37:06.619
[Man Speaking Vietnamese]

1268
01:37:10.125 --> 01:37:12.458
[Cuts Off] SHIT.

1269
01:37:28.643 --> 01:37:30.626
[Speaking Vietnamese]

1270
01:37:57.072 --> 01:37:59.221
TRIP FLARE. RODRIGUEZ'S HOLE.

1271
01:38:04.145 --> 01:38:05.895
R.P.G.

1272
01:38:08.966 --> 01:38:10.978
<i>[Man] DOC! [Rhah]
TAYLOR. FRANCIS.</i>

1273
01:38:11.002 --> 01:38:12.951
OVER HERE, MAN.

1274
01:38:13.020 --> 01:38:17.540
WHAT THE FUCK'S GOING ON?
RODRIGUEZ'S HOLE JUST GOT NAILED, MAN.

1275
01:38:17.609 --> 01:38:20.560
HERE IT IS, MAN. WE GOT GOOKS
IN THE FUCKING PERIMETER.

1276
01:38:20.628 --> 01:38:23.924
AW, SHIT. THAT'S IT. THEY
GOT THROUGH ALPHA COMPANY.

1277
01:38:23.948 --> 01:38:27.416
<i>ANYTHING BEHIND YOU THAT DON'T IDENTIFY
ITSELF, FUCKING BLOW IT AWAY, OKAY?</i>

1278
01:38:27.485 --> 01:38:30.153
FUCK. TWO: AIR
STRIKE'S COMING IN.

1279
01:38:30.221 --> 01:38:32.155
THEY'RE GONNA BE
LAYING SNAKE AND NAPE.

1280
01:38:32.223 --> 01:38:34.602
DON'T GET OUT OF YOUR FUCKING
HOLES. STAY RIGHT HERE, MAN.

1281
01:38:34.626 --> 01:38:37.126
<i>[Metallic Squeaking]</i> FUCK.

1282
01:38:38.846 --> 01:38:40.979
<i>[Squeaking Continues]</i>

1283
01:38:42.384 --> 01:38:44.300
<i>[Rhah] THEY'RE PROBING US.</i>

1284
01:38:44.369 --> 01:38:46.580
<i>THEY'LL GO DOWN THIS LINE ALL
NIGHT TRYING TO GET THROUGH.</i>

1285
01:38:46.604 --> 01:38:49.756
ALL RIGHT, STAY HERE. STAY
COOL. I'LL BE RIGHT BACK.

1286
01:38:49.808 --> 01:38:52.575
<i>[Man On Radio] WHISKEY,
FOXTROT, FOXTROT.</i>

1287
01:38:52.644 --> 01:38:55.544
[Squeaking] <i>ECHO, WHISKEY. OVER.</i>

1288
01:39:09.527 --> 01:39:11.677
WHO IS IT?

1289
01:39:13.698 --> 01:39:15.831
DON'T SHOOT! DON'T SHOOT!

1290
01:39:21.589 --> 01:39:25.029
IT'S THE AMBUSH.
OVER HERE, MAN. HURRY!

1291
01:39:27.428 --> 01:39:30.646
OH, SHIT. WATER.

1292
01:39:30.715 --> 01:39:34.266
THEY'RE ALL OVER THE PLACE.
HUNDREDS OF THEM, MOVING THIS WAY.

1293
01:39:36.370 --> 01:39:38.499
THEY WIPED US OUT, MAN.
WE DIDN'T HAVE A CHANCE.

1294
01:39:38.523 --> 01:39:40.639
WHERE'S THE C.P.? <i>BACK THERE.</i>

1295
01:39:40.708 --> 01:39:45.044
YOU GUYS GET OUT OF HERE. THEY'RE RIGHT
ON MY ASS. THEY AIN'T STOPPING FOR SHIT!

1296
01:39:47.098 --> 01:39:49.048
HEY, TAYLOR, MAN, LET'S DI DI.

1297
01:39:49.117 --> 01:39:51.116
YOU GO.

1298
01:39:57.975 --> 01:40:00.058
<i>[Gunshots]</i>

1299
01:40:00.127 --> 01:40:02.611
THERE.

1300
01:40:08.003 --> 01:40:10.035
<i>[Machine Gun Firing]</i>

1301
01:40:31.025 --> 01:40:33.025
<i>[Whistle Blowing]</i>

1302
01:40:37.515 --> 01:40:39.464
NOW HOLD IT. HOLD IT.

1303
01:40:39.533 --> 01:40:42.001
<i>[Whistle Blowing]</i>

1304
01:40:48.142 --> 01:40:50.126
<i>[Man Speaking Vietnamese
Over Loudspeaker]</i>

1305
01:40:55.316 --> 01:40:58.000
OUT OF THE HOLE! FAST!

1306
01:40:58.068 --> 01:41:00.169
<i>[Continues Speaking Vietnamese]</i>

1307
01:41:00.237 --> 01:41:03.222
GET OUT OF THE FUCKING
HOLE! THEY'RE GONNA BLOW IT!

1308
01:41:03.290 --> 01:41:06.425
LET'S GO! LET'S GO!
FOR FUCK'S SAKE...

1309
01:41:06.493 --> 01:41:09.613
FRANCIS, MOVE YOUR FUCKING
ASS! THEY'RE GONNA BLOW IT!

1310
01:41:26.163 --> 01:41:28.097
<i>[Shouting]</i>

1311
01:41:29.851 --> 01:41:31.833
FOLLOW ME.

1312
01:41:41.212 --> 01:41:43.329
<i>YOU MOTHERFUCKERS!</i>

1313
01:41:43.398 --> 01:41:45.948
<i>[Screaming]</i>

1314
01:41:46.967 --> 01:41:48.935
DIE, YOU MOTHERFUCKER!

1315
01:41:49.003 --> 01:41:51.070
[Shouting]

1316
01:41:58.630 --> 01:42:01.914
[Both Shouting]

1317
01:42:01.983 --> 01:42:03.966
IT'S FUCKING BEAUTIFUL!

1318
01:42:04.986 --> 01:42:06.969
<i>WHERE ARE YOU GOING?</i>

1319
01:42:14.829 --> 01:42:16.812
COME ON, MOTHERFUCKERS.

1320
01:42:18.549 --> 01:42:21.450
<i>[Explosions]</i>

1321
01:42:21.519 --> 01:42:23.769
COME ON! YOU CAN
DO BETTER THAN THAT!

1322
01:42:23.837 --> 01:42:26.672
THEY JUST KEEP COMING,
MAN! FUCK THIS SHIT!

1323
01:42:29.561 --> 01:42:31.481
GET BACK HERE, YOU GUTLESS SHIT!

1324
01:42:35.183 --> 01:42:38.200
[Shouting Vietnamese]

1325
01:43:01.142 --> 01:43:04.076
<i>[Man On Radio] THEY'RE
USING R.P.G.s IN OUR SECTOR.</i>

1326
01:43:04.145 --> 01:43:06.479
[Shouting]

1327
01:43:06.547 --> 01:43:09.748
<i>[Gunfire, Men
Shouting Vietnamese]</i>

1328
01:43:09.817 --> 01:43:12.129
<i>[Man On Radio] ZIPS INSIDE THE
WIRE. I REPEAT, ZIPS INSIDE THE WIRE.</i>

1329
01:43:12.153 --> 01:43:14.153
<i>WE NEED ILLUMINATION IN
THE NOVEMBER SECTOR ASAP.</i>

1330
01:43:30.805 --> 01:43:32.722
ALL RIGHT, GET ME
BRAVO RIGHT AWAY.

1331
01:43:32.790 --> 01:43:35.469
CHARLIE COMPANY REPORTS HAND-TO-HAND
ON THE PERIMETER. THEY NEED HELP.

1332
01:43:35.493 --> 01:43:38.805
OKAY, GET TWO SQUADS FROM ALPHA
DOWN THERE RIGHT AWAY. GO. GO.

1333
01:43:38.829 --> 01:43:40.946
WHERE IS THAT
GODDAMN AIR STRIKE?

1334
01:43:42.950 --> 01:43:45.711
HEY, YOU PEOPLE. WHERE
THE FUCK ARE YOU GOING?

1335
01:43:50.441 --> 01:43:52.441
[Shouting]

1336
01:44:00.534 --> 01:44:02.534
[No Audible Dialogue]

1337
01:44:04.355 --> 01:44:07.072
<i>[Wolfe] CAN'T YOU GET ANYBODY?</i>
GODDAMN IT. NEGATIVE CONTACT.

1338
01:44:07.141 --> 01:44:09.408
I CAN'T RAISE BARNES, TWO
BRAVO, TWO CHARLIE, NOTHING.

1339
01:44:09.477 --> 01:44:11.761
- GET ME SIX.
- BRAVO SIX. BRAVO SIX.

1340
01:44:11.829 --> 01:44:16.782
- IT'S DOC.
- PARKER'S HIT. GET HIM IN.

1341
01:44:20.154 --> 01:44:22.132
THEY'RE COMING THROUGH
ALL OVER. I CAN'T DO ANYTHING.

1342
01:44:22.156 --> 01:44:25.457
WHERE'S BARNES? SHIT, HE'S
DEAD. I THINK THEY'RE ALL DEAD!

1343
01:44:25.526 --> 01:44:27.688
GIVE IT UP, DOC. HE'S DEAD.

1344
01:44:27.712 --> 01:44:29.945
SIX, L.T., SIX.

1345
01:44:30.014 --> 01:44:32.781
CAPTAIN... CAPTAIN, WE'VE BEEN
OVERRUN. WE'RE PULLING BACK. OVER.

1346
01:44:32.850 --> 01:44:35.917
GODDAMN IT, LIEUTENANT. WHERE
ARE YOU GONNA PULL BACK TO?

1347
01:44:35.986 --> 01:44:37.937
THEY'RE ALL OVER THE PERIMETER.

1348
01:44:38.005 --> 01:44:42.107
NOW, YOU BE ADVISED. YOU WILL
HOLD IN PLACE AND YOU WILL FIGHT.

1349
01:44:42.176 --> 01:44:44.960
THAT MEANS YOU,
LIEUTENANT. BRAVO SIX OUT.

1350
01:45:14.175 --> 01:45:17.393
BE ADVISED, WE GOT ZIPS
IN THE WIRE DOWN HERE.

1351
01:45:17.462 --> 01:45:20.229
UH, ROGER YOUR LAST, BRAVO
SIX. CAN'T RUN IT ANY CLOSER.

1352
01:45:20.298 --> 01:45:24.015
WE'RE HOT TO TROT AND PACKING SNAKE
AND NAPE, BUT WE'LL MAKE OUR FUEL.

1353
01:45:25.019 --> 01:45:26.952
FOR THE RECORD, IT'S MY CALL.

1354
01:45:27.021 --> 01:45:29.237
DUMP EVERYTHING YOU'VE
GOT LEFT ON MY POS.

1355
01:45:29.306 --> 01:45:32.240
I SAY AGAIN, EXPEND
ALL REMAINING...

1356
01:45:32.309 --> 01:45:34.426
IN MY PERIMETER.

1357
01:45:34.495 --> 01:45:37.162
IT'S A LOVELY FUCKING
WAR. BRAVO SIX OUT.

1358
01:45:39.600 --> 01:45:42.751
<i>ROGER YOUR LAST, BRAVO
SIX. WE COPY. IT'S YOUR CALL.</i>

1359
01:45:42.819 --> 01:45:44.753
<i>GET THEM IN THEIR
HOLES DOWN THERE.</i>

1360
01:45:44.821 --> 01:45:48.757
<i>HANG TOUGH, BRAVO SIX. WE ARE
COMING COCKED FOR TREETOPS.</i>

1361
01:46:12.950 --> 01:46:14.883
BARNES!

1362
01:46:14.952 --> 01:46:16.902
<i>[Jet Engines Roaring]</i>

1363
01:46:16.971 --> 01:46:18.821
BARNES!

1364
01:46:21.459 --> 01:46:23.442
NO!

1365
01:46:23.510 --> 01:46:27.913
<i>[Jet Engines Roaring]</i>

1366
01:49:14.164 --> 01:49:16.665
GET ME A MEDIC.

1367
01:49:18.168 --> 01:49:20.602
GO ON, BOY.

1368
01:49:37.871 --> 01:49:39.871
DO IT.

1369
01:50:11.322 --> 01:50:14.156
LOOK OUT, MAD DOG. WE'VE GOT
LIVE GOOKS AT THREE O'CLOCK.

1370
01:50:14.224 --> 01:50:18.593
<i>WHAT'S DOWN HERE? LET'S GO.</i>

1371
01:50:18.662 --> 01:50:22.147
COME ON, ELMO. MOVE
YOUR FLEA-BITTEN ASS.

1372
01:50:25.186 --> 01:50:29.288
HEY, YOU OKAY? YOU ALL RIGHT?

1373
01:50:29.356 --> 01:50:31.957
CAN YOU WALK? HUH?

1374
01:50:32.025 --> 01:50:35.627
HEY, DOC! WE NEED
A MEDIC UP HERE!

1375
01:50:35.696 --> 01:50:38.697
COME ON, ELMO. COME ON,
DOC. WE GOT WOUNDED HERE.

1376
01:50:57.801 --> 01:51:01.236
MAN, THAT MUST HAVE
BEEN SOME FUCKING FIGHT.

1377
01:51:01.304 --> 01:51:03.905
YOU ALONE HERE, MAN?

1378
01:51:03.974 --> 01:51:06.241
YEAH.

1379
01:51:06.310 --> 01:51:09.244
THE BUNCH OF FUCKING
FAGGOTS. THEY ALL LEFT ME.

1380
01:51:59.663 --> 01:52:02.109
A HUNDRED AND TWENTY-TWO
WOUNDED AND STILL COUNTING.

1381
01:52:02.133 --> 01:52:05.734
<i>ESTIMATE 500
VICTOR CHARLIE K.I.A.</i>

1382
01:52:05.802 --> 01:52:08.137
<i>A HUNDRED TWENTY-TWO
AND STILL COUNTING. OVER.</i>

1383
01:52:15.262 --> 01:52:18.080
- HEY TAYLOR. THAT YOU?
- HEY, FRANCIS.

1384
01:52:18.148 --> 01:52:21.461
<i>HEY, MAN. HOW YOU DOING?</i>
I'M OKAY. HOW YOU DOING?

1385
01:52:21.485 --> 01:52:23.418
FINE, MAN. JUST
FINE. HEY, DIG IT.

1386
01:52:23.487 --> 01:52:26.087
WE TWO-TIMERS, MAN. WE
GONNA GET OUT OF HERE, BOY.

1387
01:52:26.156 --> 01:52:28.089
I'M GONNA SEE YOU
IN THE HOSPITAL.

1388
01:52:28.158 --> 01:52:30.458
WE GONNA GET A
HIGH HIGH. YES, SIR.

1389
01:52:30.527 --> 01:52:33.261
<i>SERGEANT O'NEILL.</i>

1390
01:52:33.330 --> 01:52:35.430
<i>HOW ARE YOU DOING?</i>
I'M JUST FINE, SIR.

1391
01:52:35.499 --> 01:52:38.133
WELL, THAT'S GOOD 'CAUSE
YOU GOT SECOND PLATOON.

1392
01:52:38.202 --> 01:52:41.170
YES, SIR.

1393
01:52:50.531 --> 01:52:52.681
YOU READY? YOU BET.

1394
01:53:25.499 --> 01:53:29.234
[Growling]

1395
01:54:21.805 --> 01:54:25.507
<i>[Taylor] I THINK
NOW, LOOKING BACK,</i>

1396
01:54:25.576 --> 01:54:27.592
<i>WE DID NOT FIGHT THE ENEMY.</i>

1397
01:54:27.661 --> 01:54:29.594
<i>WE FOUGHT OURSELVES,</i>

1398
01:54:29.663 --> 01:54:32.648
<i>AND THE ENEMY WAS IN US.</i>

1399
01:54:34.318 --> 01:54:36.418
<i>THE WAR IS OVER FOR ME NOW,</i>

1400
01:54:36.487 --> 01:54:38.420
<i>BUT I WILL ALWAYS BE THERE...</i>

1401
01:54:38.489 --> 01:54:40.422
<i>THE REST OF MY DAYS,</i>

1402
01:54:40.491 --> 01:54:43.274
<i>AS I'M SURE ELIAS WILL BE,</i>

1403
01:54:43.343 --> 01:54:46.979
<i>FIGHTING WITH BARNES FOR WHAT
RHAH CALLED POSSESSION OF MY SOUL.</i>

1404
01:54:49.099 --> 01:54:51.033
<i>THERE ARE TIMES SINCE...</i>

1405
01:54:51.101 --> 01:54:53.035
<i>I HAVE FELT LIKE THE CHILD...</i>

1406
01:54:53.103 --> 01:54:57.372
<i>BORN OF THOSE TWO FATHERS.</i>

1407
01:54:57.441 --> 01:55:00.075
<i>BUT BE THAT AS IT MAY,</i>

1408
01:55:00.144 --> 01:55:04.378
<i>THOSE OF US WHO DID MAKE IT
HAVE AN OBLIGATION TO BUILD AGAIN,</i>

1409
01:55:04.447 --> 01:55:07.882
<i>TO TEACH TO OTHERS WHAT WE KNOW,</i>

1410
01:55:07.951 --> 01:55:10.918
<i>AND TO TRY WITH WHAT'S
LEFT OF OUR LIVES...</i>

1411
01:55:10.987 --> 01:55:13.055
<i>TO FIND A GOODNESS
AND MEANING...</i>

1412
01:55:13.123 --> 01:55:16.124
<i>TO THIS LIFE.</i>

